Okufa okw'obudde okw'omutendera oguyita mu bwangu ogw'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19) mu European Union/ European Economic Area ne United Kingdom, nga 1 January okutuuka nga 15 March 2020
Okujjula kw'obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) kulaga enkulaakulana efaananako bw'etyo mu mawanga ga European Union/European Economic Area ne United Kingdom, ekikakasa nti wadde nga mu mitendera egy'enjawulo okusinziira ku nsi, kawumpuli wa COVID-19 akulaakulanye mangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku byokulabirako bya Italy, ensi, amalwaliro, n'ebifo eby'okubuuliramu balina okwetegekera ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekijja okwetaaga okulabirirwa n'okusingira ddala okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaaliro eddene.
Nga 31 December, 2019, waliwo abantu abawerako abaakazuulibwa nga balina obulwadde bwa kkansa mu Wuhan, Hubei, China.
Nga 9 January, 2020, ekitongole kya China eky'okufuga n'okutangira endwadde kyalagula nti ekirwadde kino kiva ku kirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva mu kirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 buyitibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obuliwo bukakasa nti abantu 80 ku buli kikumi abalina COVID-19 bafuna obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'omu mputtu z'omukka obulimu oba obutaliimu kirwadde kya kkansa, era abasinga bawona.
Mu bantu nga 14%, COVID-19 ekendeera mu bulwadde obw'amaanyi ennyo, nga kyetaagisa okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro, ate nga abantu abalala 6 ku buli kikumi bakendeera mu bulwadde obw'amaanyi, nga kyetaagisa okujjanjabibwa ennyo.
Okufa kw'abalwadde abajjanjabirwa COVID-19 kwa bitundu 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twakebera embeera eziriwo mu buli ggwanga mu European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne mu Bungereza ne tuzigeraageranya n'ezo eziri mu ssaza ly'e Hubei, China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK n'ogwa Italy wakati wa 31 January ne 15 March 2020.
Embeera za COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Oluvannyuma lw'e China, COVID-19 yasaasaana mu bitundu by'ensi, era omuwendo gwa COVID-19 mu nsi yonna gukwatagana n'ogwa China.
Nga 11 Maaki 2020, dayirekita wa World Health Organization (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde.
Magazini ya Eurosurveillance eya Maaki 5, 2020, Spiteri et al. yalaga abantu abaasooka okukakasibwa COVID-19 mu Bulaaya, okusinziira ku WHO case definition.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu abasatu abaasooka okukakasibwa obulwadde baategeezebwa Bufalansa nga 24 Jjanwali 2020 mu bantu abaali bakomyewo okuva e Wuhan, Hubei, China.
Nga 15 Maaki 2020, abantu bonna abaali bakwatibwa COVID-19 baali bakizudde mu nsi zonna 30 ez'omu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, era wakati wa Ddesemba 31, 2019 n'olunaku olwayogeddwako waggulu, abantu 39,768 be baazuulibwa era n'abantu 1,727 be baafa, nga 17,750 be baazuulibwa era n'abantu 1,441 be baafa mu Italy mwokka.
Okuzuula omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye COVID-19 n'obubonero bw'abantu abafunye obulwadde obwo
Mu European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, oguziddwa okuva mu bitundu byokka eby'obuyinza, gamba nga Minisitule y'ebyobulamu, abakungu b'ebyobulamu ab'eggwanga n'ab'ebitundu, ne WHO, guzuulibwa buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00.
Ebikwata ku COVID-19 bikozesebwa mu kunoonyereza ku mbeera eriwo mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, n'okugeraageranya ku ezo eziriwo mu Italy.
Ng'okutuukanya obuwumbi bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 ab'omugaso, twabala ennaku 14 ez'okutuusa ku mulundi abantu abafuna COVID-19 lwe bafiira, nga twekenneenya engeri COVID-19 gye yeeyisaamu mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza okuva nga Jjanwali 1 okutuuka nga Maaki 15, 2020.
Era tulaba omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazze mu buli ggwanga nga 15 Maaki 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00, era ne tugeraageranya n'ogwa Italy okuva nga 31 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 Maaki 2020.
Embeera ya COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Embeera y'ennaku 14 ez'okusaasaanya obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza mu bulambalamba yagoberera eya Hubei mu China (Ekifaananyi 1).
Mu bulambalamba, eri EU/EEA ne UK, obuwuka bwa COVID-19 bwatandika okwongera awo nga February 21 ne bweyongera nnyo awo nga February 28, 2020 (ebirala).
Kino kyakolebwa okusingira ddala olw'okweyongera okw'amangu kw'abalwadde abalagiddwa mu Italy, naye amawanga amalala gonna aga EU/EEA ne Bungereza gaalaga enkulaakulana y'okweyongera mu bungi bw'abantu abalina COVID-19 (ebintu ebirala).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza bw'ogugeraageranya ku gw'e Italy okuva nga 31 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 Maaki 2020.
Agamba nti nga 15 March ku ssaawa 8 ez'ekiro, amawanga amalala 15 aga EU/EEA ne UK gaali galabye omuwendo gw'abalwadde oguli ku kigero kya Italy okumala wiiki 3 oba wansi.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 gweyongedde nnyo mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Embeera ezirabiddwa mu bungi bw'abantu abalina COVID-19 ziraga nti kawumpuli atambula ku sipiidi y'emu mu nsi zonna.
Kino kibaawo wadde ng'ensi ezimu ziri mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, enkola z'obujjanjabi ez'enjawulo, era nga n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde mu nsi ezimu n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abajja okugezesebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okugezesebwa okw'okuddaabiriza.
Mu ntandikwa ya Maaki 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebyalumbibwa baategeezezza nti 10 ku buli 100 ku balwadde ba COVID-19 baali beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, era bannamawulire baategeezezza nti amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu bitundu ebyo byali bituuse ku busobozi bwabwe.
Ebikwata ku bantu abajjanjabibwa COVID-19 mu ddwaliro ne/oba mu ICU kati bibaawo ku mutindo gwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6 ku buli kikumi ne 1% bokka (ebitalagiddwa).
Kyokka, byandibadde bikuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okujjuzaawo ebiriko mu kulabirira abantu nga bisinziira ku muwendo gw'abalwadde abalagiddwa n'omuwendo gw'abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa wakati wa 2010 ne 2011 kwalaga enjawulo ey'amaanyi mu kuba n'endwadde za IUD n'ebisenge eby'amaanyi mu Bulaaya, okuva ku bitanda 29,2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku bitanda 4,2 mu Portugal buli bantu 100,000.
Kino kitegeeza nti amawanga gayinza okuba n'eby'okukola bingi oba bitono okusinga Italy (12,5 ebitanda bya ICU ne semi-intensive treatment ku bantu 100,000 wakati wa 2010 ne 2011).
Embeera ez'okulaga obuyinza bw'obujjanjabi, nga zirimu okuteebereza buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne UK ku bungi bw'abalwadde abajjanjabibwa COVID-19 nga balina akabi akasinga ku 90% ku buliri bw'abalwadde abajjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro, ziweereddwa mu kuddamu okw'omukaaga mu kunoonyereza kwa ECDC okw'obulabe ku COVID-19.
Olw'okuba obulwadde buno bukedde mu bitundu ebimu eby'amawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK, era nga amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi bitera okulabirira abantu ab'enjawulo, obubaka obukwata ku bulwadde n'endwadde z'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi busobola okuweebwa mu ngeri esingayo obulungi mu Nomenklatura y'Ebitundu by'Ensi (NUTS-2).
Ekyokulabirako kya Italy n'ebikolwa mu nsi endala biraga nti COVID-19 ekirwadde kyeyongedde mangu mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
N'olwekyo, ensi, amalwaliro, ne UTIs birina okwetegekera embeera ey'okusasaanya abantu SARS-CoV-2 n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kiri mu bitundu bya Italy ebikoseddwa.
Nga bwe kyalagulwa mu kunoonyereza ku kabi ka ECDC, enkola ey'amangu, ey'obuvunaanyizibwa era ey'obwenkanya nkulu nnyo okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2, nga kikyusa enkola y'okutangira eri enkola ey'okukendeeza, kubanga okwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde okwogerwako kiyinza obutakuwa kiseera kimala abalamuzi n'amalwaliro okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa mu ngeri esaanira singa tebatandikibwawo.
Okunoonyereza ku kabi ak'amangu era kulaga ebikolwa eby'obulamu obwa bonna eby'okukendeeza ku kabi akava mu kawumpuli.
Waliwo akaseera akatono amawanga mwe gasobola okwongera amaanyi mu kufuga okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 n'okukendeeza ku kukakaanya ku nkola y'ebyobulamu.
Singa ebintu bino bilemererwa, embeera y'obulamu mu nsi endala eziri mu EU/EEA eyinza okuleetawo obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Ekirwadde kya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), ekiva ku kirwadde kya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) eky'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS), kitta abantu abasukka mu 3,000 era ne kiviirako abantu abasukka mu 80,000 okukwatibwa mu China ne mu nsi yonna, ne kiviirako abantu okubonaabona.
Okufaananako akawuka ka SARS-CoV akaaleetawo SARS mu bantu nkumi na nkumi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo eyinza okusasaana okuva mu bisolo era n'eviirako obubonero obufaanana bwe bumu.
Kyokka, COVID-19 erina obulwadde obutonotono n'okufa okusinga SARS, naye y'esobola okusaasaanya ennyo, era ekosa abakadde okusinga abato, n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Mu kugoberera omuwendo gw'ebitabo ebikubibwa ku bulwadde buno obupya, ekitundu kino kisuubira okuwa amagezi ku nsonga eno ey'okunoonyereza, nga kino kigenda mu maaso amangu.
Tujja kwogera ku misingi gy'obuwuka, obuwuka, okuzuula obulwadde, okubujjanjaba, okubutegeeza n'okubukuuma.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bingi bikyalina eby'okuddamu, tusuubira nti okunoonyereza kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n'okumalawo obulwadde buno obw'akabi.
Embaga y'Omwaka mu Jjanwali 25, 2020 yafuuka ekijjukizo eky'enjawulo era ekitajja kwerabirwa eri abantu bonna ab'omu China abaategekeddwa okubeera mu kiwummulo ku lunaku lw'embaga lwonna n'olw'emyezi egiwerako olw'obulwadde obuggya obw'akawuka.
Akawuka kalifaanana nnyo ne coronavirus (CoV) eyaleetawo ekirwadde kya SARS mu 2003; n'olwekyo, kaayitibwa SARS-CoV-2 ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) nga 11 Febwali 2020, era obulwadde bwakyo ne buyitibwa CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Ekirwadde kino kyatandika mu kibuga Wuhan ekya China, era ne kibuna mangu mu ggwanga lyonna n'okutuuka mu nsi nga 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Okutuusa nga Maaki 2, 2020, akawuka kaali kaviiriddeko abantu abasukka mu 80,000 okukakasibwa okuba nga balina COVID-19, nga basukka mu 40,000 bawonye era nga basukka mu 3,000 bafudde.
WHO yalabula nti COVID-19 ye "mulabe wa bantu omukulu", era asobola okuba ow'amaanyi okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu myezi egitawera ebiri, ebitundu ebisukka mu 200 bifulumiziddwa ku COVID-19, omuli obusawo bw'obusawo, obulwadde, obuwuka, okwekebeza n'okujjanjaba, okuva alipoota esooka eyafulumizibwa nga January 7, 2020, eyalaga engeri akawuka gye kaawanguddwa mu balwadde abangi.
Ekitundu kino kigezaako okuwunzika enkulaakulana mu kunoonyereza ku kitundu kino ekippya ekikulaakulana amangu.
Buli lwe kiba kyetaagisa, tujja kugeraageranya COVID-19 ne SARS n'obulwadde obulala obuva ku CoV, Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, kawumpuli wa 2012).
Era tujja kwogera ku bye tuyize okutuuka kati ku bukuumi n'okumanya obulwadde, awamu n'ebibuuzo ebirala eby'amaanyi.
CoVs zitwalibwa okuba endwadde ezitafa ku bantu, nga ziviirako ebitundu 15 ku buli kikumi eby'endwadde z'omukka.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tulabye emirundi ebiri abantu abalina obulwadde bwa CoVs, nga bano be SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, eyaviirako obulwadde obwatandika mu China mu 2003 ne mu Saudi Arabia mu 2012, era amangu ddala ne busaasaana mu nsi endala ezitali zimu n'obulwadde n'okufa eby'entiisa.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 eyaliwo kati ye kawumpuli ey'okusatu ey'ekirwadde kya CoV mu byafaayo by'omuntu.
Nga bwe kiragibwa mu kifaananyi 1,1, omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba pneumonia abatamanyiddwa gye baava gwatandika okutegeezebwa mu Wuhan nga 31 December, 2019 eri ekitongole kya China eky'ebyobulamu.
Nga wayise ennaku musanvu, ekitundu ekikwata ku ngeri CoV gye yalagibwamu kyafulumizibwa.
Nga Jjanwali 15, 2020, omulwadde eyasooka okufa okuva e Wuhan yategeezebwa.
Mu kiseera kye kimu, ekirwadde kino kyabuna mangu mu bibuga, amasaza n'ensi eziriraanyewo.
Nga Jjanwali 20, obulwadde bw'abakozi b'ebyobulamu bwalagibwa, ekiraga nti abantu basobola okusasaana.
Nga January 23, ekibuga Wuhan kyazingibwawo, nga n'entambula yonna ey'abantu bonna ekomeddwa.
Nga January 24, okunoonyereza okwasooka ku bulwadde buno kwalaga nti ku balwadde 41 abaakakasibwa nti balina obulwadde buno, 21 bokka be baaliko akakwate n'akatale k'ebibala by'ennyanja akali mu Wuhan, akaatwalibwa okuba nti ke katandikiddewo obulwadde okuva mu nsolo.
Nga January 30, WHO yalangirira ekirwadde kino ng'embeera ey'obudde ey'amaanyi ey'ensi yonna.
