Omuwendo gw'abantu abakwatiddwa obulwadde bwavudde ku 23 January, 2020, nga kino kye kiseera eky'entambula y'abantu mu China ng'Embaga y'Omwaka ogujja tennatandika.
Obusaasizi bw'abalwadde abaakakasibwa bwali 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10% - 1.86%), era okufa kw'abalwadde bonna okwalagulwa kwali 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02% - 4.59%).
Ebintu ebisatu ebikulu ebiviirako akabi ka COVID-19 kwe basajja (abasajja), emyaka (abasoba mu myaka 60), n'omusujja gw'amawuggwe omunene.
CoVs y'ekika ky'akawuka akagazi ak'enjawulo akalina ensingo emu eya RNA.
Zisobola okugabanyizibwamu ebika bina, okuli: alpha, beta, gamma ne delta, nga alfa coronaviruses ne beta coronaviruses zimanyiddwa okuggya abantu.
Glycoprotein (S) ey'omu nsawo ekwata ku bakwasisa baayo aba angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ECA2) ne dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ku SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, era oluvannyuma enkulakulana y'ensiri n'ebaawo.
Genome ya RNA eya siriimu efulumizibwa mu cytoplasm; oluvannyuma lw'okwekubisa genome ya virus, genomic RNA nga erimu glycoproteins ez'omu nsawo ne nucleocapsid proteins efulumya obusawo obulimu virions, nga bweyunga ku plasma membrane ne zifulumya akawuka.
Enkula y'ekika kya SARS-CoV-2 eyasooka yategeezebwa nga January 10, 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 yakizuula nti ngeri mpya eya betacoronavirus nga erina ebika by'obutonde ebisukka mu 99.98% mu byokulabirako 10 eby'enjawulo ebyaggibwa mu kifo kye kimu eky'okusaasaana, akatale k'ebibala by'ennyanja aka Huanan mu Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 erina enkulaakulana y'ekika ekyenkanankana ne SARS-CoV okusinga MERS-CoV.
Nga bakozesa ekikozesebwa mu kulaba ebintu ebinene, baakizuula nti SARS-CoV-2 erimu ebitundu eby'amaanyi eby'omubiri.
ECA2 ey'omuntu yakizuula nti ye yakkiriza SARS-CoV-2, era ne SARS-CoV.
Kyokka, protein S eya SARS-CoV-2 ekwatagana ne protein ECA2 ey'omuntu mu ngeri etegudde lubege okusinga eya SARS-CoV, ekikwatagana n'okuba nti SARS-CoV-2 evunaanyizibwa obulwadde obutono mu balwadde okusinga SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okufuuka protein empya empi ekoleddwa orf3b ne protein ey'ekika ekisooka ekoleddwa orf8.
Orf3b eya SARS-CoV-2 esobola okubaako ky'ekola mu bulwadde bw'akawuka era n'okulemesa IFNβ okwogera; kyokka, orf8 terina kifo oba nsonga emanyiddwa.
Nga 18 Febwali 2020, Zhou, et al., baategeezezza nti ECA2 ey'obuwanvu bwonna ey'omuntu erina obugolokofu bwa 2,9 Å mu kizibu ekirina omutambuzi wa amino acid B0AT1.
Kyasangibwa nti ekizibu, ekyalimu ebitundu ebigguddewo n'ebitali biggule, kyali kigabanyiziddwa wamu ng'ekika kya dimer, era ekizibu kya ECA2-B0AT1 kisobola okukwataganya obutoffaali bwa S bubiri, ekiraga obujulizi obw'okumanya n'okusannyalala kwa CoV.
B0AT1 esobola okufuuka ekiruubirirwa eky'okujjanjaba eddagala erigema endwadde ya SARS-CoV-2.
Omusolo oguva mu ndagabutonde n'omutaasa
SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV byombi bimanyiddwa nti byava mu balongo ne bitwalibwa mu bantu nga biva mu bisolo ebiriko obuwuka obuyitibwa civet ne eŋŋamira.
Okuyitira mu kugeraageranya SARS-CoV-2 ne CoV endala, abalwadde b'ensiri be balabiddwa ng'abazannyi ba SARS-CoV-2, kubanga akawuka akapya kaliko enjawulo ya 96% ku CoV bbiri ez'ensiri eziringa SARS ez'ekika kya bat-SL-CoVZX45 ne bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Kyokka, omulabirizi ow'omunda eyayamba akawuka okuyita mu bifo eby'enjawulo n'okulumba abantu akyalabika, era ekkubo ly'okusasaanya terinnazuulibwa.
Ji, et al., bagamba nti emisota gy'etwala akawuka okuva ku musota okudda mu bantu, nga kino kyetaagisa okuzzaawo omutindo gwa S.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza, abanoonyereza mu Guangzhou, China, baalagidde nti ebinyonyi ebiwaawaatirwa ebirye enkuyege era ebikozesebwa ennyo mu ddagala ly'omu China, bye bisobola okuleeta SARS-CoV-2, okusinziira ku ngeri emu gye bifaananamu mu bitundu 99 ku buli kikumi wakati wa CoV eyazuulibwa mu binyonyi ne SARS-CoV-2.
