Ebintu eby'omubiri n'ebya kkemikale ebya SARS-CoV-2 tebinnamanyibwa.
SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV zisobola okuwangaala mu bitoola okumala essaawa 48 mu kifo ekikalu era n'okutuusa ennaku 5 wansi wa 20 °C n'obusaasi bwa 40-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuba n'ebintu ebifaanagana.
Kyategeezeddwa nti SARS-CoV-2 ekwatibwako ekitangaala kya UV n'ebbugumu lya 56 °C okumala eddakiika 30; ether, 75% ethanol, ekirungo ekirimu ekirungo, peracetic acid, chloroform n'ebirungo ebirala naye nga si chlorhexidine, bikola bulungi mu kumalawo akawuka.
Mu bulambirira, abantu bonna tebalina bukuumi eri SARS-CoV-2 era bwe kityo, batwalirizibwa akawuka akapya.
Mu kiseera kino tewali kunoonyereza kwonna ku ngeri omuntu gy'ayanukamu obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 kwe kwogerwako.
N'olwekyo, tusobola okwekenneenya ebitundu eby'edda eby'obujjanjabi ku CoV endala, naddala SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV (Fig. (Fig.4).4).
Mu bulambirira, oluvannyuma lw'akawuka okuyingira mu muntu, kano kakkirizibwa okusooka mu mubiri gw'omuntu okuyitira mu bikolwa eby'omubiri okuzuula ebikwatirwa mu mubiri, omuli lectin type C, Toll type receptor (TLR), NOD type receptor (NLR), ne RIG-I receptor (RLR).
Okuyitira mu makubo ag'enjawulo, akawuka kano kayamba mu kwogera ebintu ebiviirako obulumi, ebirungo by'ensiri okukula, n'okufulumya interferons ez'ekika I (IFNs), ezikendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa kawuka kano era ne zireetera amaziga agava mu biwuka ebyo okukulaakulana.
Kyokka, protein N eya SARS-CoV esobola okuyamba akawuka okudduka obulwadde.
Mu kaseera katono, obulwadde obwo bujja kweyongera okulwanyisa akawuka ako.
T lymphocytes omuli CD4+ ne CD8+ T cells zirina ekifo kikulu mu kulwanirira.
Obutoffaali bwa CD4+ T buleetera obutoffaali bwa B okukola obuwuka obumu obutta akawuka, ate obutoffaali bwa CD8+ T buzikiriza butereevu obutoffaali obuliko akawuka.
Obutoffaali bwa T obukolagana ne bulonda obutoffaali obuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, CoV esobola okulemesa ebikolwa bya T-cell nga ereetera T-cell okuvunda.
Obulwadde bw'omubiri, omuli n'obutonde obujjanjaba obulwadde obuyitibwa C3a ne C5a, nabwo bukulu nnyo mu kulwanyisa obulwadde bw'akawuka.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, abalwadde abaawonawo bwe baafunanga eddagala erigema akawuka ka MERS-CoV, baavunaanyizibwa.
Ku luuyi olulala, obulwadde bwe bweyongera, obusosoze buvaamu ebirungo ebingi ebiyinza okwonoona amawuggwe n'ebitundu ebirala eby'omubiri, era mu mbeera embi ennyo, ebitundu by'omubiri bingi bisobola okuvunda, oba n'okufa.
Obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV-2, obuzingiramu okulabika kw'obubonero mu bantu, businga kukosa bannamukadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi n'abakazi ab'embuto.
Abantu abalina obuwuka bungi oba abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu mubiri batera okufuna obulwadde buno okusinga abantu abalala.
Ekiseera eky'okwekweka ekya SARS-CoV-2 kya nnaku 1 okutuuka ku 14, era emirundi egisinga ennaku 3 okutuuka ku 7, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku bantu 425 abaasooka mu Wuhan.
Kyokka, okunoonyereza ku bantu 1,099 kwalaga nti ekiseera eky'okwekweka kyali kya nnaku ssatu, ku muwendo ogweyongedde, era nga kyava ku nnaku 0 okutuuka ku 24.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko awo, nga bwe kyogeddwako waggulu, kulaga nti ekiseera eky'okwekwekaalirira kyali ennaku 4.8 (3.0 - 7.2) okusinziira ku bantu 8,866.
Kikulu nnyo abakungu b'ebyobulamu okukyusa ekiseera eky'okusibibwa mu ddwaliro okusinziira ku kiseera ekituufu eky'okusiba, bwe kityo ne kiziyiza abantu abalina obulwadde obutaliimu bubonero okuleeta kawuka eri abantu abalala.
Ng'empisa eya bulijjo, abantu abafunye akawuka oba abakakwatiddwa, batera okwetaagibwa okubeera mu ddwaliro okumala ennaku 14.
Ekiseera ky'okusibibwa kirina okuyongerwako ennaku 24?
Omusujja gutera okuba akabonero akasooka era akasinga obukulu aka COVID-19, akayinza okujja kokka oba nga kayambiddwa obubonero obulala, gamba ng'okukoowa, okubulwa omukka, obulumi mu mibiri, okweraliikirira, omutwe, obulumi mu bulago, okukaaba, obulumi mu kifuba, okukaaba, okukaaba n'okusaanuuka.
Abalwadde abamu baafuna dyspnea ne/ oba hypoxemia wiiki emu oluvannyuma lw'okwoleka obubonero bw'obulwadde.
Mu mbeera enzibu, abalwadde baakulaakulana mangu ne bafuuka n'obulwadde obw'okuwummulamu, ne bafuna obuwuka obuyitibwa septic shock, metabolic acidosis, ne coagulopathy.
Abalwadde abalina omusujja n'obubenje n'omusujja ogw'amaanyi, wadde nga tebalina buzibu mu kulaba ebifaananyi by'omutima, balina okwekebejjebwa akawuka okusobola okuzuulibwa mu bwangu.
Okunoonyereza ku bantu mu nkomerero ya December 2019 kwalaga nti ebitundu by'obubonero byali 98% ku lubuto, 76% ku kasasiro, 55% ku dyspnea, ne 3% ku lubuto; 8% ku balwadde baali beetaaga obuyambi mu kuzzaamu omukka.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kuno byabadde bifaanagana mu kunoonyereza okubiri okwakolebwa mu maka n'omu ku abo abafunye obulwadde buno.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2012 kwalaga nti abalwadde ba MERS-CoV nabo baalina omusujja (98%), okukankana (47%) ne dyspnea (55%) ng'obubonero obukulu.
Kyokka, abalwadde 80 ku buli kikumi baali beetaaga obuyambi mu kuddamu okuwummula, okusinga abalwadde ba COVID-19, nga kino kiva ku kufa okw'amaanyi okuva ku MERS bw'okugeraageranya ne COVID-19.
Obulwadde bw'omuka (26%) n'obulumi mu bulago (21%) nabyo byalabikira mu balwadde ba MERS.
Mu balwadde ba SARS, omusujja (99% okutuuka ku 100%), okukkuluma okukaaba (29% okutuuka ku 75%), okubulwa omukka (40% okutuuka ku 42%), okukaaba (20% okutuuka ku 25%) n'obulumi mu bulago (13% okutuuka ku 25%) byalagibwa okuba obubonero obukulu, era okubudaabuda kwawalirizibwa abalwadde nga 14% okutuuka ku 20%.
Okutuusa nga Febwali 14, omuwendo gw'abafa COVID-19 gwali 2%, ng'abalwadde abazuuliddwa mu nsi yonna batuuse ku 66,576.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, okufa kwa SARS okutuuka mu Noovemba 2002 kwali 10% ku bantu 8,096 abaakakasibwa.
Ku MERS, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu June 2012, okufa kwaliwo kwa bitundu 37 ku buli kikumi ku bantu 2,494 abaakakasibwa.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko awo kwalaga nti omuwendo gw'abantu abazaala SARS-CoV-2 R0 gwali gwa 6.47 nga guli ku 95%, okuva ku 5.71 okutuuka ku 7.23, ate R0 ya SARS-CoV yali ya 2 okutuuka ku 4.
Okugeraageranya SARS-CoV-2 ne MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV ku bubonero bwazo, okufa n'omutindo gwa R0 kulagiddwa mu Tabula Tabula1.1.
Ebifaananyi ebiri waggulu biraga nti SARS-CoV-2 esobola okusaasaana okusinga MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV, naye si ya kabi nnyo okusinga ezo ebbiri ez'oluvannyuma.
N'olwekyo, kizibu nnyo okufuga obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 okusinga MERS-CoV ne SARS-CoV.
Okulabika kw'obubonero mu bantu bangi kitera kubaawo mu maka gamu oba mu bantu oba mu mmotoka emu, gamba ng'eryato.
Abalwadde batera okuba nga baagenda mu Wuhan oba mu bitundu ebirala ebikwatiddwako, oba nga baaliko abantu oba abalwadde abafunye akawuka mu wiiki bbiri ez'emabega ng'obubonero tebunnaba kulabika.
Kyokka, kyalagiddwa nti abantu basobola okutwalibwa akawuka okumala wiiki ezisukka mu bbiri nga tebalina bubonero, era abalwadde abawonye era ne bava mu malwaliro bayinza okuddamu okukwatibwa akawuka, ekireetawo okweraliikirira okwongera ku kiseera eky'okusibibwa.
Abalwadde balina omuwendo gwa ssaddaaka oba omuwendo gwa ssaddaaka gwa ssaddaaka.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, lymphopenia ng'omuwendo gwa ssero eryeru oguli wansi wa 4 x 109/L omuli n'omuwendo gwa ssero eririmu ssero eriri wansi wa 1 x 109/L, n'emisingi emingi egy'aspartate aminotransferase ne viremia byazuulibwa mu balwadde 1,099 abalina COVID-19.
Enzimu n'obutonde bw'omubiri n'omusaayi byabadde bya maanyi nnyo mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abamu, ate C-reactive protein n'obutonde bw'ensiri byabadde bya maanyi nnyo mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abasinga.
Mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi, omuwendo gwa D-dimer, ekikolebwa mu musaayi nga guvunnama okuva mu fibrin, gwali gwa maanyi era omuwendo gwa balwadde ba lymphocyte gwali gukendeera.
Obulwadde bw'ekisenge ekitali kya bulijjo bubeerawo mu balwadde abasinga abalina COVID-19, era bubeera n'ebizikiza ebitali bya bulijjo oba ebirabika ng'ebirabika obulungi mu biwundu.
Abalwadde batera okufuna obulwadde bwa kkansa, obulwadde obw'omu kifuba n'obulwadde bw'omu kifuba.
ADRS bw'ebawo, obulumi obuba buzzeemu, amazzi ne gajjula, n'obulwadde bwa fibrosis obugenda bweyongera, biviirako omuntu okubulwa omukka.
Obulwadde bw'omulembe ogusooka n'ogwokubiri buviirako omukka oguyitibwa surfactant okukendeera n'okweyongera ku bbugumu eriri ku mubiri, ne kiviirako omukka okutalika, era ne kiviirako omubiri okugwa.
N'olwekyo, ebivaamu ku bifaananyi eby'ekisenge ekinene bitera okuba nga birina akawuka.
Nga 18 Febwali 2020, okunoonyereza okwasooka okwa COVID-19 kwalaga nti waliwo obutoffaali bw'omukka, ekisenge kya hyaline, obutoffaali bw'omubiri obuyitibwa interstitial lymphocyte n'obutoffaali obwa syncytial mu biwundu by'omulwadde eyafa obulwadde buno, nga kino kikwatagana n'obulwadde bw'akawuka ka siriimu ne ARDS, era nga bwe kiri mu balwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Okukebera RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 nga tukozesa polymerase  reverse transcriptase chain reaction (RT-PCR) kyakozesebwanga ng'ekigendererwa ekikulu mu kunoonyereza ku COVID-19.
Kyokka, olw'ebisaanyizo eby'obulimba ebingi, ebiyinza okwanguya obulwadde, obulwadde bwatandika okukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza (nga tebukoma ku RT-PCR yokka) mu China nga Febwali 13, 2020.
Embeera efaananako bw'etyo yaliwo ne bwe baakizuula nti omuntu alina obulwadde bwa SARS.
N'olwekyo, okugatta ebyafaayo by'obulwadde, obubonero bw'obulwadde, ebigezo by'omu ddwaliro n'ebivudde mu bubonero bwa radiology kikulu nnyo okusobola okufuna obulwadde obulungi.
Nga 14 Febwali 2020, ekibiina kya Feng Zhang kyalaga enkola ey'okukozesa enkola ya SHERLOCK, eyeesigamiziddwa ku CRISPR, okunoonyereza ku SARS-CoV-2, ekinoonyereza ku bitundu bya RNA ebyakolebwa okuva ku SARS-CoV-2 mu 20 x 10-18 mol/L okutuuka ku 200 x 10-18 mol/L (10 okutuuka ku 100 kopi ku microliter y'omwenge) nga bikozesa omuggo mu ssaawa nga emu, nga tebyetaagisa byuma bya maanyi.
Tusuubira nti enkola empya esobola okwongera ku busobozi n'obwangu bw'okukozesa singa ekikeberebwa mu bibala.
Olw'obutaba na bumanyirivu ku CoV empya, abasawo basobola okuwa abalwadde ba COVID-19 obujjanjabi obw'ekika ekya waggulu nga bagezaako obujjanjabi obw'enjawulo obwakozesebwa oba obwayogerwa edda okujjanjaba CoV endala nga SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV n'endwadde endala ez'akawuka (Laba (Labaali2).2).
Okujjanjaba kuno kuzingiramu eddagala erikola kati n'erigenda okukozesebwa, nga mw'otwalidde eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka, eddagala erikendeeza ku bulwadde bw'omubiri, eddagala eriyitibwa steroids, plasma y'abalwadde abawonye, eddagala ly'omu China, n'okuyamba mu by'omwoyo.
N'omusaayi gw'abalwadde abawonyezza obulwadde buno guleeteddwa ng'obujjanjabi.
Kkampuni z'eddagala zidduka n'ebiseera okuzimba eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka n'omulwadde.
SARS-CoV-2 esingira ddala erumba amagumba mu kusooka era kirabika era erumba, mu kigero ekitono, ebitundu ebirala ebirimu ECA2 nga ekitundu ky'omubiri n'ennyingo.
Kyokka, obulemu mu mpumu n'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri bye bisinga okuleetera abalwadde okufa.
N'olwekyo, obuyambi mu kuddamu okuwummulamu bukulu nnyo mu kukendeeza ku bubonero n'okuwonya obulamu, era buzingiramu okujjanjaba okusaasaanya omukka gwa oxygen, okusaasaanya omukka gwa oxygen, okufuuyira omukka ogutabaako bulabe, n'okufuuyira omukka ogw'amaanyi okusinziira ku bunene bw'obulwadde.
Abalwadde abalina obubonero obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu beetaaga okufuna okusiiga omukka mu mubiri (ECMO), enkola endala ey'okujjanjaba obulwadde bw'omutima oba obw'okuwummulamu.
Okugatta ku ekyo, okukuuma obuwumbi bw'amasannyalaze, okutangira n'okujjanjaba endwadde ez'olukale n'okwekamirira, n'okukuuma ebitundu by'omubiri ebikulu nabyo bikulu nnyo eri abalwadde ba SARS-CoV-2.
Kitegeerekeka nti cytokine cascade eva ku by'omubiri okwongera okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa SARS ne MERS.
Cytokine cascade ngeri ya kuddaabiriza kwa mubiri, nga kwe kuleeta cytokines omuli TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, ne MCP-1.
Zino zisobozesa obutoffaali bw'omubiri okwekutula ku bulwadde okufulumya ebirungo ebingi, ebireeta obulwadde bwa ARDS n'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri bingi.
Okuziyiza obulwadde bw'omubiri kikulu nnyo mu bujjanjabi bw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebiyitibwa cytokine cascades, naddala mu balwadde abakambwe.
Ebintu ebiyitibwa corticosteroids ne tocilizumab, ekirwanyisa ekirwadde kya IL6 ekikola ku mubiri gumu, bikozesebwa okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa cytokine cascade.
Okujjanjaba okulala okw'okuziyiza obulwadde bw'omusujja gw'ensiri okuli okukyusa obusobozi bw'omubiri obw'okuddamu mu bulwadde bw'ensiri za T; okuziyiza IFN-y, IL-1, ne TNF; okuziyiza JAK, blinatumomab; okuziyiza cytokine 4; n'okuziyiza HDAC.
Steroids, nga immunosuppressants, zikozesebwa nnyo mu bujjanjabi bwa SARS okukendeeza ku buzibu bw'okusaanuuka.
Kyokka, eddagala erikola eddagala eriyitibwa steroids teryavaamu kalungi konna eri abalwadde abalina SARS ne COVID-19 olw'okufuna obuvune obw'amaanyi mu mawuggwe.
Zisobola okuleeta obuzibu obw'amaanyi, naddala osteonecrosis avascular, ne kikosa nnyo obulwadde.
Kyokka, eddagala eriyitibwa corticosteroids ery'akaseera katono mu ddwaaliro eriri wansi okutuuka ku kkomo ly'eddagala lino lyasiimibwa nnyo nga lirina okukozesebwa n'obwegendereza mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abalwadde ennyo.
Mu kiseera kino eky'okuwandiika, tewali ddagala liyinza kumalawo bulwadde buno.
Kyokka, okugaba remdesivir mu musaayi, ekika kya nucleotide, kyazuulibwa okuba nga kya mugaso mu mulwadde wa Amerika alina COVID-19.
Remdesivir ddagala eriggya erirwanyisa akawuka eryafulumizibwa Gilead, eryali lirina okusooka okujjanjaba endwadde eziva ku Ebola ne Marburg.
Oluvannyuma remdesivir era yalaga nti esobola okulemesa obuwuka obulala obuyitibwa simple ribbon RNA, omuli MERS ne SARS.
Okusinziira ku kino, Gilead yawa China ekirungo kino okukola ebigezo ku bantu abalina akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2, era ebivudde mu kukebera bino binnyonnyolwa nnyo.
Okugatta ku ekyo, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ ritonavir, ne ribavirin byalagiddwa ng'obujjanjabi obuyinza okuweebwa abalwadde abalina obubonero obw'okuwummulamu obw'amaanyi.
Obulwadde bw'omukaba, okulumwa, okusaanuuka, obuzibu bw'omubiri n'ebirala biyinza okubaawo oluvannyuma lw'okufuna eddagala eriyitibwa lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Enkolagana y'eddagala lino n'eddagala eddala eryakozesebwa mu balwadde eryo erina okwekeberebwa ennyo.
Plasma y'abalwadde abawonye era n'okuleeta obuwuka obwa bulabe
Okukuŋŋaanya omusaayi okuva mu balwadde abawonye obulwadde obw'akabi okujjanjaba abalwadde abalala abalina obulwadde obwo, oba okukuuma abantu abalamu obulungi obutagwa lubege, kya ddaaki.
Mu butuufu, abalwadde abawonyezebwa batera okuba n'omutindo omunene ogw'omubiri oguyingira mu musaayi gwabwe.
Antibodies ye immunoglobulin (lg) ekolebwa B lymphocytes okulwanyisa endwadde n'ebirala ebitalina kye bikolawo, era zimanya obuwuka obuli mu ndwadde ne buzibulako butereevu.
Okusinziira ku kino, plasma yakuŋŋaanyizibwa okuva mu musaayi gw'ekibiina ky'abalwadde abaawonyezebwa COVID-19, era n'eteekebwa mu balwadde 10 abaali mu mbeera embi.
Obubonero bwe bwagenda bukyuka mu ssaawa 24, ng'okusaanuuka n'omukka gwa virus bikendedde, era n'omusaayi gwe gukendeera.
Kyokka, okukakasa n'okutangaaza byetaagisa okusobola okusalawo okukozesa enkola eno ku kigero ekinene nga tetunnakola bulwadde bwa njawulo.
Ate era, olw'ebikolwa eby'obujjanjabi, ebizibu ebimu ebiva mu plasma biteekwa okwekenneenyezebwa n'obwegendereza.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuwuka obuziyiza obulwadde busobola okuleetera omuntu okwekutula ku bulwadde obwo n'aleeta obulwadde obuyitibwa cytokine release syndrome, obuyinza okumuviirako okufa.
Okuba n'omubiri ogumenyese mu musaayi kitera okuba ekitono, era n'okwetaaga plasma kwa maanyi okujjanjaba abalwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Kizibu okuteekateeka n'okufulumya obuwuka obukwata ku muntu mu bwangu okusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu nsi yonna.
N'olwekyo, kikulu nnyo era kya muganyulo nnyo okwawula obutoffaali bwa B okuva mu balwadde abawonye era n'okumanya obubonero bw'ekika ekikola ku bulwadde obwo oba okunoonyereza ku bulwadde obwo.
Mu ngeri eyo, tusobola okwongera ku bungi bw'omubiri oguyitibwa antibody.
Eddagala ly'omu China ery'obuwangwa, TCM, libadde likozesebwa okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka okujjanjaba endwadde ez'enjawulo mu China.
Kyokka, ebikolwa byabyo byesigamye nnyo ku kugatta awamu ebintu bingi mu ngeri eyeeyawula ku ngeri y'okunoonyereza ku bulwadde okusinziira ku njigiriza za TCM.
Ebisinga obungi ku bintu ebikola obulungi tebimanyiddwa oba tebimanyiddwa bulungi kubanga kizibu okuggya n'okumanya ebikola obulungi oba enkuŋŋaana zaabwe.
Mu kiseera kino, olw'obutaba na bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19 obutuufu era obw'omuganyulo, TCM efuuse ekimu ku bujjanjabi obusinga okuweebwa abalwadde abalina obubonero obutonotono oba obw'omutindo oba abalwadde abawonye obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, kapuloozi za Shu Feng Jie Du ne Lian Hua Qing Wen zaalabiddwa nga nnungi mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Ebisale ebisinga obulungi eby'abalwadde ba COVID-19 byalabikira mu ssaza ezitali zimu mu China ezaakozesa TCM mu 87% y'abalwadde, omuli Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) ne Hunan (50%), ate ssaza lya Hubei, erikozesa TCM mu 30% byokka eby'abalwadde ba COVID-19, lyafuna ebisale ebisinga obutono (13%).
Kyokka, kino kizibu kubanga waliwo ebintu bingi ebizingirwa mu kunoonyereza, gamba ng'omuwendo gw'abalwadde n'obulwadde.
Nga Febwali 18, 2020, Boli Zhang ne banne bafulumya okunoonyereza okwageraageranya obujjanjabi obw'Ebugwanjuba obwakozesebwa mu bujjanjabi obw'enjawulo n'obujjanjabi obw'Ebugwanjuba obwakozesebwa mu bujjanjabi obw'enjawulo n'obujjanjabi bwa TCM.
Kyakakasiddwa nti ebiseera ebyetaagisa okuzzaawo ebbugumu ly'omubiri, okuwonya obubonero n'okusigala mu ddwaliro byali bitono nnyo mu abo abajjanjabibwa eddagala ery'omu Bulaaya n'eddagala lya TCM okusinga abo abajjanjabibwa eddagala ery'omu Bulaaya lyokka.
Omuwendo gw'obulwadde obw'amaanyi ennyo (okuva ku butono okutuuka ku bwa maanyi) gwali mutono nnyo mu kibiina ekikozesebwa eddagala lya Bulaaya n'eddagala lya TCM okusinga mu kibiina ekikozesebwa eddagala lya Bulaaya lyokka (7.4% versus 46.2%), era okufa kwali kutono mu kibiina ekikozesebwa eddagala lya Bulaaya n'eddagala lya TCM okusinga mu kibiina ekikozesebwa eddagala lya Bulaaya lyokka (8.8% versus 39%).
Kyokka, obutuufu n'obutebenkevu bwa TCM bikyalina okunoonyerezebwa mu bifo ebirala bingi era ku kigero ekisingawo.
Era kyandibadde kya muganyulo okunnyonnyola engeri gye bakolamu ebintu era n'okunnyonnyola ebizingirwa mu bujjanjabi bwa TCM oba obugatta ku bujjanjabi obwo.
Abalwadde abakakasibwa oba abakeberezebwa okuba n'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 batera okutya ennyo obulwadde obuyitibwa COVID-19 era obuyinza okuba obw'akabi ennyo, era abantu abali mu kifo ekyesudde nabo bawulira obuteewuunya, ekiwuubaalo, n'obusungu.
Okugatta ku ekyo, obubonero bw'obulwadde obuyitibwa ssenyiga omukambwe, okukaaba, n'okukoowa, awamu n'ebizibu ebiva mu bujjanjabi, gamba ng'okuloota olw'omwenge oguyitibwa corticosteroids, bisobola okuleetera omuntu okweraliikirira ennyo n'okweraliikirira ennyo.
Mu ntandikwa y'ekirwadde kya SARS, obulwadde obw'omubiri obuwerako, omuli obwennyamivu obutaggwaawo, okweraliikirira, okutya, okukaaba, obubonero bw'obutafa, okwegomba okubi n'okwegomba okwetta byalagibwa.
Okuzuula abantu n'okubateeka mu ddwaliro ng'ekitundu ky'ebyo gavumenti by'ekola okulwanyisa COVID-19 kiyinza okuleetera abantu okweraliikirira ennyo, era bayinza okuwulira omusango olw'ebyo ebiva mu kuyingira, okuteekebwa mu ddwaliro, n'okuswala okuleetebwa ku b'eŋŋanda zaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
N'olwekyo, obujjanjabi bw'obwongo bulina okuweebwa abalwadde ba COVID-19, abantu abalowoozebwa okuba n'obulwadde n'abantu abaabadde nabo, awamu n'abantu bonna abali mu bwetaavu.
Obuyambi mu by'omwoyo bulina okuzingiramu okussaawo ebibinja by'abasawo ab'enjawulo, okutegeeza abantu ebikwata ku bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'enteekateeka z'obujjanjabi, n'okukozesa ebyuma ebikozesebwa mu by'obulamu okwewala abantu okukwatagana.
Ensigo ez'omugaso nkulu nnyo mu kuggyawo ekkubo ery'okusindikibwa okuva mu bisolo n'abantu abalina obulwadde eri abantu abayinza okubulwa obulwadde, era zitera okuwewula ku ddagala erirwanyisa akawuka mu kufuga kawumpuli ak'akawuka.
Enkola zikoleddwa okuzimba eddagala eryesigamiziddwa ku protein S okuleeta obuwuka obuziyiza obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV era/oba obukuuma obulwadde.
Ensigo zigezeseddwa mu by'ensolo ku SARS.
Kyokka, obumanyirivu mu bulamu bw'abalwadde bano mu bantu abakulu era n'engeri gye bawonya n'obukuumi bwabwe okuva ku bulwadde bwa virus ez'ekika ky'omuntu, bikyalina okusooka okunoonyerezebwa nga tetunnatandika kunoonyereza.
Kino kirabika kiva ku kuba nti SARS yabula emyaka 17 bukya era tewali mulwadde mulala yenna eyazuulibwa okuva olwo.
Ku luuyi olulala, obulwadde bwa MERS obutali bumu n'obulwadde bwabwo bweyongera mu bitundu bya Buwalabu era ne busaasaana mu bitundu ebirala olw'ebitundu omuli endwadde z'ensolo.
Enkola z'okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa MERS ezikozesebwa mu bulwadde buno, ze zaakolebwa nga bakozesa obuwuka obutaliimu, plazmids za DNA, ebitundu eby'obutwa, nanoparticles, ebitundu ebiringa obuwuka, n'ebitundu by'amagi ebizze bifuulibwa, era ebimu byateekebwako mu bisolo.
Okukulaakulanya eddagala eriruma era erikola obulungi erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 eri abantu abatalina bulwadde buno mulimu gwa bwangu era mukulu nnyo mu kufuga ekirwadde kino.
Kyokka, kizibu okuvvuunuka obuzibu, olw'ekiseera ekiwanvu (emyezi 18, ku mulamwa) ekyetaagisa okukulaakulanya eddagala n'enkyukakyuka mu ngeri y'okukulaakulanya CoV.
Ng'obulwadde obupya, COVID-19 yatandika okweyoleka mu bujjuvu, nga ekosa enkumi n'enkumi z'abalwadde.
Mu mbeera ezisinga obungi, abalwadde bawona mpolampola nga tewali kizibu kyonna.
Kyokka, okufaananako SARS ne MERS, COVID-19 era erina akakwate n'obulwadde n'okufa okw'amaanyi mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
N'olwekyo, okuzimba ekyokulabirako eky'okulangirira obulwadde kikulu nnyo eri ebitongole by'ebyobulamu okusobola okukulembeza obuweereza bwabwe, naddala mu bitundu ebirimu obuzibu.
Okusinziira ku by'okunoonyereza ebibaddewo, ebintu bino wammanga biyinza okukwata oba okubaako kye bikola ku kulwala abalwadde ba COVID-19 (Laba (Laba) Lulabo33):
Emyaka: Emyaka kye kintu ekisinga obukulu mu kulabula kwa SARS, era ne COVID-19.
COVID-19 esinga kukosa abantu abali wakati w'emyaka 30 ne 65, nga 47,7% ku balwadde bali waggulu w'emyaka 50, mu kunoonyereza ku bantu 8,866, nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Abalwadde abaalina obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi baali basinga okubeera n'obulwadde obw'amaanyi n'ebizibu, era baali bakulu nnyo okusinga abalwadde abataalina bujjanjabi obw'amaanyi (nga bali mu myaka 66 nga boogera ku myaka 51), ekiraga nti emyaka gyabakubiriza okufuna obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Ekika: SARS-CoV-2 yafuna abasajja bangi okusinga abakazi (0.31/100,000 abasajja ne 0.27/100,000 abakazi), nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Embeera n'ebizibu: Abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi baba n'obubonero obw'amaanyi obw'okufuna obulumi bw'omutima oba arrhythmia.
Obulwadde bw'omutima kye kyaviirako abantu okufa ennyo olw'obulwadde bwa SARS.
Kyategeezeddwa nti SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okukwata ku cholangiocytes ez'omulongoofu ez'ECA2, ekiyinza okuvaako obulemu mu kibumba mu balwadde abalina COVID-19.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti emyaka n'endwadde eziriwo bikwatagana bulungi era bisobola okutabangula buli kimu.
Ebivudde mu kukebera ebitategeerekeka: omuwendo gwa C-reactive protein (CRP) mu musaayi gukakasa obuzibu bw'okusaakaanya oba obuvune mu bitundu by'omubiri era gwalagibwa ng'ekintu ekiragirira obulwadde, obuvunanyizibwa ku bujjanjabi n'okuwona.
Enkolagana wakati w'omutindo gwa CRP n'obuzibu n'okulaga obulwadde bwa COVID-19 nayo yayanikiddwa.
Ate era, okulinnya kwa lactate hydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), ne creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bisobola okuyamba mu kulabula.
Enzime zino ziri mu bitundu by'omubiri bingi, naddala omutima n'ekibumba, era zifulumizibwa nga waliwo obulemu mu bitundu by'omubiri.
N'olwekyo, bino bye bintu ebimanyiddwa ennyo ebiraga obulwadde bw'omutima oba obw'ekibumba.
