Olw'okuba eddagala erya waggulu ery'obutiti ery'omubiri lyeyongera nnyo mu balwadde abalina obulwadde bwa SARS obw'amaanyi, bangi ku abo abaawonawo baafuna obulwadde bwa osteonecrosis avascular, ne kibaleetera obulemu obutaggwaawo n'obulamu obw'obutaba bulungi.
N'olwekyo, singa kiba kyetaagisa, eddagala eriyitibwa steroids lisaanidde kukozesebwa mu bungi obutonotono era okumala ekiseera kitono mu balwadde abalina COVID-19.
