Enkolagana ya kawuka ne musawo ku by'okusasaanya
Ng'oggyeko ebintu ebisatu eby'obulabe ebyogeddwako waggulu, okukwatagana kw'obulabe n'omulabirizi y'ekintu ekirala ekikulu ekireetera abantu okuyitibwa endwadde.
Wano, okuzza awamu kwa SARS-CoV kutwalibwa ng'ekyokulabirako ekikulu, ekiraze obujulizi bw'okulonda obulungi mu biseera eby'okusasaanya.
Okusinziira ku kugezaamu okwawulawo wakati w'abantu n'ebisolo bya SARS-CoVs, SARS-CoV ekkirizibwa okukyusa amangu mu bantu ab'enjawulo, naddala n'enkyukakyuka mu DLR ya pulasitiini S.
Mu bulambirira, DLR ku proteini ya S eya CoV ekolagana n'omutambuzi wa ssimu era esunsulwa nnyo antibody response y'omulabirizi.
Mu SARS-CoV, DLR eri ku amino acid 318th okutuuka 510th mu S1 ekitundu ekikwatagana ne ECA2 y'omuntu era n'ebikwatagana n'obutwalibwa bw'akawuka.
DLR ya SARS-CoV esobola okutegeera ebikwatako ECA2 mu nsolo ezitali zimu omuli ennyama, ennyama, empiso, n'embwa, ekireetera abantu okuyisaamu akawuka.
Mu butuufu, kyazuulibwa nti amino acid mukaaga zokka ze zaali za njawulo ku za bantu n'ez'ebisolo bya civet mu DLR, era nnya ku zo zaali mu ngeri y'okusiba omutindo gwa ECA2.
SARS-CoV okuva mu civet erina enkulaakulana K479N ne S487T mu DLR yaayo, ekiyinza okwongera ku busobozi bwa protein ya spike okwenyigira mu muntu ECA2 receptor.
Mu ngeri endala, amayinja gano abiri ag'omu butonde gasobola okuba nga gasobola okuleetera abantu okukyusa endwadde zaabwe.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti SARS-CoV-2 erina omutikkiti gwe gumu ne SARS-CoV.
Enjawulo ya 30% wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne SARS-CoV mu S1 unit ya S protein eraga nti obusobozi bwa S protein yo obw'okusiba ne ECA2 bw'omuntu busobola okuba nga bwakyusibwa.
Mu butuufu, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa n'obutonde kulaga nti waliwo enkolagana ey'amaanyi wakati w'ekika kino emirundi 10 oba 20 okusinga wakati wa ECA2 ey'omuntu n'enfuna ya SARS-CoV S.
Era kijja kuyamba okumanya oba waliwo ekirala ekirina akakwate n'okussa SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu.
Ekyewuunyisa, HCoV-NL63 nayo ekwata ku ECA2, naye n'ekitundu ekirala eky'amagi S.
Waliwo ebitundu ebirala eby'omusujja gwa HCoV, gamba nga aminopeptidase N eri HCoV-229E ne 9-O-acetyl sialic acid eri HCoV-OC43.
Era biyinza okuba nga bivunaanyizibwa ku ngeri CoV ezo gye zitambulamu obulungi mu bantu oluvannyuma lw'okusasaana okuva mu nsolo.
Ng'oggyeko abagenyi, obubonero bw'obuwuka obuyitibwa HCoVs buva ku bantu abalala.
Okwawukana kwa protein zino ez'omulabirizi wakati w'abantu n'abalabirizi ba HCoV aba bulijjo ng'ennyenje, embuzi, n'ensiri kiyinza okulemesa abantu okuyisaamu.
HCoVs zirina okuwamba ebintu ebiruma omulabirizi n'okulemesa ebintu ebiruma omulabirizi okusobola okuleetawo okusaasaana obulungi wakati w'ebika.
Mu ngeri eyo, ebirambikizo by'obutonde mu kitundu kino ekikulu eky'okukwatagana kwa virus n'omulabirizi bikyalina okunoonyerezebwa n'okutegeerekeka.
Okukebera okutali kwa njawulo ku mutendera gwa genome ku buzibu bw'omulabirizi n'ebintu ebikugira SARS-CoV-2 nga tukozesa tekinologiya wa CRISPR ow'omulembe kiyinza okuvaamu ebibala ebirungi.
Okujja kwa HCoVs empya: kudda ku mutindo gwazo ogusooka
Enjawulo mu CoV z'ennyenje ewa omukisa omungi HCoV empya okujjawo.
Mu ngeri eyo, CoV z'ennyenje zikola ng'omuzira gwa HCoVs.
Ate era, okukyuka amangu n'okuggyawo obuwuka nabyo bireetera HCoV okukulaakulana era nga bino bye bintu ebibiri ebikulu mu nkola eno.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, okufuna oba okufiirwa obutoffaali obuggya obuteekawo proteini kiyinza okukyusa ennyo obuntu bwa virus.
Mu bupolyetini obuyambako SARS-CoV, ORF8 ekkirizibwa okuba ekikulu mu kukyusa abantu okuva bwe kiri nti obuwuka bw'ennyama bw'ensiri obukwata ku SARS-CoV bwawukanako naye ne kizuulibwa nti buwandiika bupolyetini bwa ORF8 obw'enjawulo.
Ekimu ku bintu ebikosa abantu kwe kuba nti SARS-CoVs ezirimu nucleotide 29 zaaliko ebitundu by'omubiri eby'enjawulo.
Okusazaamu kugabanyamu ORF8 ne kugabanyamu ORF8a ne ORF8b, era kisuubirwa nti nkyukakyuka ey'okwegattako ekubiriza okukyuka kw'omugenzi.
Ate era, SARS-CoV erina ebyafaayo by'okussa mu nkola n'ebika bya alphaCoVs ne gammaCoVs, omuli ebitundu ebitonotono eby'okussa mu nkola eby'enjawulo eby'omulembe oguyitibwa RNA polymerase.
Ebifo eby'okuggyawo nabyo byazuulibwa mu nsp9, mu bitundu ebisinga ebya nsp10 ne mu bitundu bya nsp14.
Mu ngeri y'emu, ekirwadde kya MERS-CoV kyalagibwa nti kyafuna obuwuka obw'enjawulo, nga buno bwaliwo mu bisolo bya kkamera mu Saudi Arabia.
Ng'oggyeko SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, ebikolwa eby'okuggyawo ebirwadde byalabiddwa ne mu HCoV endala, HCoVs mwe zigattibwa ne CoV z'ebisolo ebirala mu buwangwa bwazo.
Ate era, kikulu okukijjukira nti okulonda okw'ekika kiyinza okuleetera abantu okukyusa mu ndagabutonde y'akawuka, oboolyawo nga kiva ku kukendeeza ku kukemebwa kwa kawuka, gamba ng'okukemebwa kw'omubiri.
Ekyokulabirako ky'ebyo bye bimu ku bivaako kwe kufiirwa ORF4 empanvu mu kika kya HCoV-229E olw'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu bibiri eby'ekika.
Wadde nga ORF4 etatwalibwako kabi kayinza okulabikira mu bulwadde bwa HCoV-229E obuli mu bisolo by'ennyenje ne ku ŋŋamira, alphaCoV eya alpaca erina obubonero bw'obutoffaali obumu obuyingizaamu obuwuka obuyitibwa nucleotide, ne kivaamu enkyukakyuka mu bifaananyi.
Ekisembayo naye ekisinga obukulu, enkulaakulana y'obuwuka obupya obuyitibwa HCoVs nayo ekulemberwa okupikirizibwa mu bantu ababufuna.
Tewali bubonero oba obubonero obutonotono bwokka bwe bwalabikako mu balongo nga balwadde CoVs, ekiraga nti CoVs n'abalongo beegasse.
Kirabika abalongo beeyisa bulungi ku CoVs mu ngeri y'omubiri n'omubiri.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obulemu mu kukubiriza obuyambi mu bulwadde bw'ensiri bukendeeza ku bulwadde obuva ku CoV.
Ate era, ebikolwa by'emibiri gy'ensolo ezitta abantu mu mbuzi bikoseddwa olw'okukyusa omutonzi w'emibiri gy'ensolo ezitta abantu NKG2/CD94 era n'olw'obutaba na maanyi ga molekyo ez'ekika I ez'ekika ekikulu eky'obutakkiriziganya.
Ate era, omuwendo omunene ogw'ebika by'omukka ogukolera ku musaayi (ERO) ebiva mu bikolwa by'ensiri eby'amaanyi bisobola okulemesa abantu okuzaala CoV era n'okukyusa ekirungo kya exorribonuclease, ne kibawa amaanyi okuzaala obuwuka obuleeta endwadde bwe bayingiza mu muntu omulala.
Endwadde ezisingawo ez'obulabe ez'omu CoV nazo zisobola okukulaakulana nga zikwatagana, ne kiviirako obutoffaali oba engeri empya ez'obutoffaali okufuuka ez'omulabirizi.
N'olwekyo, tekiri kya butanwa nti HCoVs ssatu empya zaafuluma mu myaka 20 egiyise.
CoVs tezirwadde, oba ziviirako obubonero obutonotono mu bantu abazirimu, gamba ng'ennyenje n'eŋŋamira.
Bakola enkulaakulana ey'amaanyi nga tebaleesewo buzibu bwa maanyi mu mubiri.
Ekiwandiiko kino kirimu okunnyonnyola ku kuzuula abajjanjabi abatalina bubonero n'ensonga lwaki abantu bafuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Obubonero obw'amaanyi businga kuva ku buzibu bw'omubiri obw'okwerinda n'obw'okukozesa obusimu obuyitibwa cytokine cascade, nga bwe buba bungi, obuzibu bw'omubiri obwo bwe businga okuba obw'amaanyi.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, mu abo abatalina bubonero, obulwadde buno tebukyasobola kweyongera kweyongera.
Enkola y'emu ey'okuggyawo obuwuka obw'omubiri eyinza okuba n'ebirungi mu bujjanjabi bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Obuyambi bwa interferon bwa maanyi nnyo mu bisolo.
N'olwekyo, okugaba interferon eya kika I mu kutandika kw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu kirina okuba eky'omuganyulo.
Ate era, okwenyigira mu bulwadde bwa NLRP3 mu bisolo tebirina kalungi konna.
Nga tugoberera endowooza eyo, okuziyiza ekirwadde kya NLRP3 ne MCC950 kiyinza okuba eky'omuganyulo mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Okujja kwa SARS-CoV-2 kugoberera emisingi gye gimu SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV gye zaavaayo.
Wadde nga betaCoV y'ennyenje yazuulibwa okuba nga yeegatta ku SARS-CoV ku kigero kya 95%, waliwo CoV y'ennyenje eyeegatta ku SARS-CoV-2 ku kigero kya 96%.
Wadde nga kisangiddwa nti ebinyonyi n'ebisolo ebirala mu katale birina obuwuka obwenkanankana ne SARS-CoV, abazannyi ab'omutawaana aba SARS-CoV-2 tebategerekese.
BetaCoVs okuva mu pangolin, ezirina obumu obw'amaanyi ne SARS-CoV-2, zaasangibwa, ekiraga nti pangolin ziyinza okubeera ng'omu ku bazannyi ab'omutawaana, oba betaCoVs okuva mu pangolin ziyinza okuyambako mu buwumbi bw'ebitundu by'omubiri mu SARS-CoV-2.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bikyaliwo, tewali bukakafu bulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yajjawo butereevu oba mu bugenderevu.
CoVs zikomyewo mu nsi yonna olw'ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 ekivuddewo.
Okunoonyereza ku CoV mu balanga n'ebisolo ebirala kyakyusa nnyo endowooza yaffe ku bukulu bw'ensolo eziri mu nsolo n'ebisolo ebirimu HCoVs mu kuyita wakati w'abantu.
Obujulizi obucaase bulaga nti SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, ne SARS-CoV-2 zaava mu nkima era ne zisasaana mu bantu nga ziyita mu bantu abalala.
Olw'okuba obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV bwatandikira ku bantu n'ebinyonyi mu butale, okuggyawo obutale n'okutta ebinyonyi mu butale obwo kyandisobozesezza okukomya ekirwadde kya SARS.
Nga tugoberera enkola y'emu, ebinyonyi byandiggiddwa mu butale obw'ebitundu eby'amazzi okusobola okuziyiza endwadde ez'ekika ky'ensolo, olw'okuzuula ebika by'ebinyonyi bingi ebya betaCoVs ebikwatagana ne SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, tekinnaba kutegeerekeka mu kunoonyereza okujjawo oba SARS-CoV-2 ekwattibwa abantu okuyitira mu pangolin n'ebisolo ebirala ebirina amata, era n'engeri gye bikwattibwamu.
Ku luuyi olulala, MERS-CoV emaze ebbanga ddene mu bisolo.
Eŋŋamira zino zikola ng'entambula enkulu, era ze nsibuko enkulu ey'ennyama, amata, engoye n'ebyoya by'endiga eri abantu b'omu kitundu.
Zisangibwa mu bitundu bya Buwalabu ne Afirika.
N'olwekyo, tekisoboka kutta ŋŋamira zonna okuziyiza MERS, nga bwe kyali mu butale bw'ensolo enkambwe mu China okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okumalawo endwadde za MERS eziddamu, enkola yonna erina okukolebwa okukulaakulanya eddagala erigasa ku MERS-CoV eri eŋŋamira, nga lirina okukwataganyizibwa n'enteekateeka endala ez'okuziyiza endwadde.
Olw'okuba tetusobola kumalawo bulwadde buno, waliwo endwadde endala eziyinza okuvaamu.
Waliwo endwadde za CoV ez'enjawulo eziva mu nsolo.
Naddala, CoV z'ennyenje ezirina obusobozi bw'okuleeta endwadde za zoonotic za njawulo nnyo.
Waliwo obusobozi bungi nti CoVs zino ez'ekisolo ziyinza okukulaakulana era ne zikwatagana, ne kivaamu CoVs empya ez'akabi ennyo era/oba ez'akabi eri abantu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Enkola y'okulya ensolo enkambwe mu bitundu ebimu mu China erina okulekera awo okukendeeza ku kukwatagana okutali kwa mugaso wakati w'abantu n'ensolo.
Olw'ebizibu bya SARS, MERS ne COVID-19, enteekateeka ennungi ey'okuddamu n'okwetegekera erina okukolebwa.
Mu butuufu, waliwo obuwuka bungi obw'akabi ku nsi okumala ekiseera kiwanvu.
Basigala mu bifo byabwe eby'obutonde okutuusa lwe wabaawo omukisa ogw'okusengukira mu bika ebirala.
Wadde ng'ennyenje zirina engeri nnyingi ezireetera akawuka okusaasaana, abantu bwe bayigirizibwa okuziviirako, basobola okukendeeza ku mikisa gye bafuna nga bakolagana n'ennyenje n'ebisolo ebirala eby'omu nsiko.
Okufuba okw'okweyongera okulondoola ebisolo by'ensolo kyetaagisa okusobola okutegeera obulungi ebikwata ku bulamu bw'abantu n'obw'abantu ababeera mu nsolo, era ekyo kijja kutuyamba okwewala endwadde okuva mu nsolo okuyingira mu bantu.
Okufundikira, engeri esinga obulungi ey'okutangira obulwadde bwa zoonotic kwe kusigala wala n'abantu okuva mu bifo ebirimu obuwuka bwa zoonotic.
Ebintu bingi eby'ekyama ekikwata ku nsibuko ya SARS-CoV-2 bikyaliwo.
Okusooka, singa abalongo basindika akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 eri abalongo, kikulu okumanya embeera abalongo n'abalongo mwe bayinza okubeera mu kifo kye kimu.
Ekyokubiri, singa abalongo bakola kinene nnyo mu kussa akawuka ku bantu, abantu balina okumanya engeri gye bakolagana n'abalongo.
Ekyokusatu, singa ensolo endala ey'ekika kino erina ekifo ky'omulabirizi ow'omunda, engeri gy'ekolagana n'ebika eby'enjawulo, omuli abantu, abalongo n'ebisolo ebiyitibwa pangolins, erina okutangaaza.
N'ekisembayo, okuva ebisolo ebirabika ng'ebirina ebisolo ebingi, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebisolo eby'awaka, bwe biyinza okuba nga birina obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, okulondoola awamu n'okunoonyereza ku bulwadde birina okukolebwa.
Bw'oba oli musota, pangolin oba ensolo endala, ssuubi nti SARS-CoV-2 oba obuwuka bwa bazadde bwayo obufaanana ennyo bujja kulabikamu mu bantu ababubeeramu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi mu kitundu kino kujja kulaga engeri SARS-CoV-2 gye yeeyambisamu mu nsolo, nga kino kirina amakulu mu bukuumi n'okufuga COVID-19 mu bantu.
Ebiragiro by'okunoonyereza ku 'bulwadde obwesigika' ne 'bulwadde obukakasiddwa' bwa COVID-19 byetaaga okuvuganyisibwa
Nga February 6, 2020, ttiimu yaffe yafulumya ekitabo ekiraga engeri y'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba akawuka ka coronavirus aka 2019 (2019-nCoV). Ekitabo kino kyogera ku bumanyirivu bwaffe era kye kirimu amagezi amalungi ag'okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino.
Kyokka, ekirwadde kya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kipya. Okutegeera kwaffe n'okumanya kweyongera mpolampola okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okw'omuddiriŋŋanwa n'okwolesebwa mu nkola y'ekisawo; olw'ensonga eyo, enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Mu bbaluwa eno, tuddamu ekyewuunyo ku bukulembeze bwaffe era tuwa enkola y'okunoonyereza eya "bulwadde obwekeberezebwa" ne "obulwadde obwekakasibwa" okusinziira ku Bulagirizi obw'Okulondoola n'Okutereeza COVID-19 (obw'omusanvu) obwasindikibwa Akakiiko k'Eby'obulamu aka National Health of the People's Republic of China.
Mu Ddesemba 2019, akawuka ka coronavirus aka 2019 (2019-nCoV) kaaleetawo ekivudde mu bulwadde, nga kati kayitibwa akawuka ka coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), era akawuka kano kayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga 11 Maaki 2020, WHO yatandikawo COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde.
Okusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yatandikawo ekitabo ekiraga engeri y'okukozesa eddagala eryo ekyafulumizibwa ku mukutu gwa Intaneeti mu lupapula lw'amawulire oluyitibwa Military Medical Research nga Febwali 6, 2020.
Ekitabo kino kifunye nnyo abantu bangi okuva lwe kyafulumizibwa.
Kyokka, weetegereze nti COVID-19 ndwadde empya. Okutegeera kwaffe n'okumanya kweyongera mpolampola okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okw'omuddiriŋŋanwa n'okwolesebwa mu nkola y'ekisawo; olw'ensonga eyo, enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, ebiragiro by'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 ebyafulumizibwa National Health Committee of the People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) wakati wa January 16, 2020 ne March 3, 2020 byafulumizibwa mu nnamba musanvu nga birimu enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu bimu ku byo.
Omukulembeze waffe kati afunye ebigambo okuva eri Zhou et al., eyawa amagezi ku nsonga ennyangu okusinziira ku bumanyirivu bwe yalina mu ddwaliro.
Omulimu guno gwongedde obujulizi obupya mu bukulembeze bwaffe era era guwa obukakafu obw'omugaso ku kawumpuli ono ow'ensi yonna.
Tukkiriziganya n'omulimu gwabwe omukulu era ne twebaza.
Kyokka, omulimu gwabwe gwetaaga okuddaabirizibwa okusinziira ku bulagirizi obuggya obw'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 (enkyusa ey'omusanvu ey'okugezesebwa) n'ebyenjigiriza ebipya.
