Omulimu guno gwaleetawo obwetaavu bw'emmere y'abaana mu butale obumu era oluvannyuma ne guwereddwa gavumenti ya Australia. Wadde nga waliwo abantu bangi abalina COVID-19 mu bukiikakkono bwa Italy ne mu kitundu kya Wuhan, era nga waliwo n'ebyetaago eby'emmere, ebifo bino byombi tebyalina njala.
Ebintu ebyakolebwa China ne Italy okulwanyisa eby'obugagga ebikolebwa mu ngeri etali ya mu mateeka n'okusuubula eby'obugagga byavaamu ebirungi, ne kiziyiza ebbula ly'emmere eryali lisuubizibwa mu Bulaaya ne mu Amerika.
