Okuva COVID-19 lwe yatandika, wabaddewo okweyongera kw'obusosoze, obusosoze bw'ab'amawanga amalala, n'obusosoze eri abantu abava mu China oba mu buvanjuba bwa Asiya, era n'eri abantu ab'omu bitundu eby'obulabe mu Bulaaya, Amerika n'ensi endala.
Ebintu eby'entiisa, obutategeeragana, n'obukyayi byalabikira mu nsi nnyingi, naddala mu Bulaaya, ebuvanjuba bwa Asiya, Amerika ow'omu bukiikakkono, ne mu kitundu kya Asia Pacific.
Ebivudde mu February (ng'abalwadde abasinga bakyali mu China) byalaga enneewulira z'obusosoze ezaayolesebwa mu bibiina ebitali bimu okwetooloola ensi nti abantu b'omu China bagwanidde okufuna akawuka kano oba okubonerezebwa olw'ebyo bye baakola.
