Ebigezo bya laboratory by'obulwadde bw'omukka oguva mu kirwadde kya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) n'akawuka ka SARS - CoV-2 omuli enkola ez'okumanya obuwuka n'ez'okumanya obuwuka obuva mu bulwadde.
Okubeerawo kwa kawuka mu bibala kukakasibwa RT-PCR, ekikebera RNA ya coronavirus.
Okugezesa kuno kwa njawulo era kukolebwa ku kumanya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 yokka.
Kikozesebwa okukakasa obulwadde obubaddewo oba obubaddewo.
Okuzuula obulwadde (serology) kiyinza okukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza n'okwetegereza abantu.
Okugezesebwa kwa antibody kulaga abantu bameka abafunye obulwadde, nga mw'otwalidde n'abo abalina obubonero obutonotono ennyo obutabaako bubaka oba abataalina bubonero.
Omuwendo omutuufu ogw'okufa kw'endwadde n'omutindo gw'obutabaako bulwadde mu bantu guyinza okussibwawo okuva mu bibala by'okugezesebwa okwo.
Olw'okukebera okutono, mu Maaki 2020 tewali ggwanga eryalina bubaka bwesigika ku buwumbi bw'abantu abaliko akawuka.
Nga 23 Maaki, tewali ggwanga lyonna eryali ligezezza abantu abasukka mu 3 ku buli kikumi, era waliwo enjawulo nnyingi mu bungi bw'okugezesa mu mawanga.
Okusoomoozebwa kuno kuyinza okwongera okukosa ebisale by'abantu abafa ku bulwadde obuba buzze buzuulibwa, naye nga mu nsi ezimu busobola okuba nga businga obungi.
Nga tukozesa enkola ya real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), okugezesa kuyinza okukolebwa ku by'omukka ebiggiddwa mu ngeri ezitali zimu, omuli okubbamu ensiri oba okubala amalusu.
Ebyava mu kunoonyereza bino bitera okulabika mu ssaawa ntono oba ennaku bbiri.
Okugezesa kwa RT-PCR okwakolebwa n'okusiiga mu bulago bw'omumwa kwe kwesigika mu wiiki esooka y'obulwadde.
Oluvannyuma, akawuka kayinza okubula mu bulago nga bwe kakyongera okugaziya mu biwundu.
Eri abantu abalina akawuka abagezeddwa mu wiiki ey'okubiri, eky'okubiri, ebintu okuva mu bifaananyi biyinza okuggibwa wansi mu mpenda z'omukka nga bikozesebwa mu kugoba oba ebintu ebifulumiziddwa mu ngeri y'okufulumya biyinza okukozesebwa.
Ekimu ku bigezo bya PCR ebyasooka kyatandikibwawo mu Charité mu Berlin mu Jjanwali 2020 nga kikozesa enkola ya real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), era kye kyesigamiziddwa ku bukodyo 250,000 obugabiddwa ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu ekya World Health Organization (WHO).
Bungereza nayo yakola ekigezo nga 23 January 2020. Kampani ya South Korea Kogenebiotech yakola ekigezo, ekikozesebwa mu kuzuula SARS-CoV-2 nga kiva ku PCR (PowerCheck Coronavirus) nga 28 January 2020.
Okunoonyereza kuno kuno kunoonyereza ku musaayi gwa "E" oguba guli mu bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe, era n'omusaayi gwa RdRp oguli mu SARS-CoV-2. Mu China, BGI Group kye kimu ku bizinensi ezisoose okufuna olukusa okuva mu China National Medical Products Administration olw'ekikozesebwa mu bwangu mu kunoonyereza ku SARS-CoV-2 nga kikozesa PCR. Mu Amerika, ekitongole kya CDC (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention) kigabira ebitongole by'ebyobulamu ebijjanjaba abantu eddagala lya RT-PCR (RT-PCR) erya Corona Virus (2019-nCoV) eri mu kiseera ekituufu.
Ekimu ku bikeberebwa ebisatu eby'ekika ku bitabo eby'edda eby'okugezesa kyaleetawo okugezesebwa okutali kwa nnamaddala olw'ebirungo ebikyamu, era n'okulemesa okugezesa ku CDC mu Atlanta; kino kyaviirako empeke ezisoba mu 100 buli lunaku okutegekebwa obulungi mu mwezi gwonna ogwa Febwali 2020.
Okugezesa nga kukozesa ebitundu bibiri tekwali kwesigika okutuusa nga Febwali 28, 2020, era oluvannyuma lw'ekyo, laboratories z'ebitundu ne z'essaza zaakkirizibwa okutandika okugezesa.
Okugezesebwa kwaweebwa olukusa okuva mu Food and Drug Administration wansi w'okukkiriza okukozesa mu bwangu.
Okutandika nga March 5, 2020, LabCorp yalangirira nti waliwo okugezesebwa kwa COVID-19 okwesigamiziddwa ku RT-PCR mu ggwanga lyonna.
Quest Diagnostics era yafuula ebigezo bya COVID-19 nga bifunibwa mu ggwanga okuva nga Maaki 9, 2020.
Tewali kizingiramu bungi; okukungula n'okukola ku byokulabirako birina kukolebwa okusinziira ku bisaanyizo bya CDC.
Mu Russia, ekigezo kya COVID-19 kyatandikibwawo era ne kifulumizibwa State Research Center mu Virology ne Biotechnology, VECTOR.
Nga 11 Febwali 2020, ekigezo kyawandiisibwa ekitongole kya Federal Health Surveillance Service. Nga 12 Maaki 2020, Mayo Clinic yagamba nti yali akoze ekigezo ekikebera obulwadde bwa COVID-19. Nga 13 Maaki 2020, Roche Diagnostics yafuna olukusa okuva eri FDA olw'ekigezo ekiyinza okukolebwa mu ssaawa 3.5 ku kigero ekinene, bwe kityo ne kisobozesa ekyuma okukola ebigezo nga 4,128 mu ssaawa 24.
Nga 19 March 2020, FDA yawa olukusa lwa Emergency Use (USA) eri Abbott laboratories olw'okugezesa ku Abbott's m2000 system; FDA yasooka kuwa olukusa Hologic, LabCorp, ne Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Nga 21 March 2020, Cepheid era yafuna USA okuva mu FDA olw'okugezesebwa okutwala eddakiika nga 45.
FDA yakkiriza ekigezo ekikozesa tekinologiya w'okunyweza nucleic acid mu kifo kya PCR.
Olw'okuba tekyetaagisa kuzzeemu kuzzeemu kuzzeemu kuzzeemu, enkola eno esobola okuleeta ebibala mu ddakiika ttaano zokka ate n'ebibala mu ddakiika 13.
Mu kiseera kino waliwo ebyuma nga 18,000 mu Amerika era Abbott asuubira okwongera ku mulimu gw'okugaba ebigezo 50,000 buli lunaku. Okugezesa okukozesa ekirwanyisa ekirwanyisa ekirwadde ekimu era ne kukikwataganya n'ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekiggya kwe kukubibwa mu Taiwan, nga basuubira okuwa ebivudde mu ddakiika 15 oba 20 ng'okugezesa okw'omukka.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu March 2020 kwalaga nti "ebifaananyi bya x-ray eby'omu kifuba tebirina bukulu bwa maanyi mu kulaba obulwadde mu kiseera we bukoma, ate ebizuulibwa mu CT biyinza okuba nga byaliwo ng'obulwadde tebunnaba kutandika".
Ebintu ebitera okulabika mu CT bizingiramu ebitaala bya multilobaric mu kiraasi ekimera ekirimu ennyuma, enjuyi n'ebweru.
Obukulembeze bw'ekisenge, okuzimba n'okunyweza biva ku bulwadde.
Okunoonyereza okwageraageranya PCR ne CT mu Wuhan mu kifo ekirimu ekirwadde kino kyalaga nti CT ya maanyi okusinga PCR, wadde nga si nnungi, nga bingi ku bifaananyi byayo bikwatagana n'obulwadde obulala obw'olukonvuba n'enkola z'obulwadde.
Okuva mu Maaki 2020, American College of Radiology ekubiriza nti "TC tegirina kukozesebwa mu kukebera oba ng'ekigezo ekisooka okukebera COVID-19". Okuva mu Maaki 2020, CDC ekubiriza PCR ng'ekigo ekisooka.
Ekimu ku bikolwa by'omubiri okuziyiza obulwadde kwe kufulumya ebirwanyisa omuli IgM ne IgG.
Bino biyinza okukozesebwa mu kulaba obulwadde mu bantu obwatandika ennaku 7 oba amangu ddala ng'obulwadde bwatandise, okunoonyereza ku bulwadde, n'okwetegereza abantu.
Enkola ez'obukozesebwa mu nkola ez'obukozesebwa mu malwaliro mangi zijja kusobola okukola ebigezo bino, naye okubeerawo kwabyo kujja kwesigama ku bungi bw'ebintu ebiba bifulumidde.
Okwejjanjaba obulwadde bwa CLT, ekiraamo kimu eky'omusaayi oguyitibwa peripheral blood kye kikozesebwa, wadde nga waliwo ebiraamo bingi ebiyinza okukozesebwa okukebera obulwadde.
Okukola PoCT, omusaayi gumu gufunibwa mu buwunga.
Okwawukana ku nkola ya PCR, ekitundu ky'okukuŋŋaanya tekyetaagisa nga tonnagezesebwa. Nga Maaki 26, 2020, FDA yalonda ebitongole 29 ebyategeeza ekitongole nga bwe kyetaagisa, era okuva kati bisobola okugaba ebigezo byabwe eby'omubiri.
Nga 7 Apuli 2020, ekigezo kimu kyokka kye kyakkirizibwa FDA nga kirina olukusa olw'okukozesa mu bwangu. Mu nkomerero ya Maaki 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics ne Epitope Diagnostics baafuna obukusa bwa Bulaaya ku bikozesebwa byabwe eby'okugezesa, ebiyinza okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa HIV mu musaayi.
Obusobozi bw'okugezesa bukubisaamu ebitundu ebikumi na bikumi mu ssaawa ntono era nga buno businga amangu okugezesa kwa PCR okw'omulembe okw'obusawo bwa RNA.
Obuwuka buno buzuulibwa mu nnaku 14 oluvannyuma lw'okulwala. Mu April, Bungereza yakizuula nti tewali na kimu ku biwuka ebigezo eby'obulabe bye baagula kyali kisaanira okukozesebwa.
Hong Kong yateekateeka enkola abalwadde abateeberezebwa okuwona basobola okusigala awaka, "ekitongole ky'obutebenkevu kijja kuwa omulwadde akatoffaali k'okunoonyereza", balina okufulumya amalusu mu katoffaali, ne bakakyuusa ne bafuna ebivaamu oluvannyuma lw'akaseera katono. NHS y'e Bungereza yalangirira nti ekola enteekateeka y'okunoonyereza ku balwadde abateeberezebwa mu maka, ekiggyawo akabi k'omulwadde okutegeeza abalala singa bagenda mu ddwaliro oba obwetaavu bw'okusaasaanya eddagala ku ambulensi singa eggyamu. Mu kukebera kwa ddwaaliro ku COVID-19 ku balwadde abateeberezebwa, omusawo akolera ku by'okunoonyereza ng'akola ku by'okunoonyereza.
Ebifo eby'okuvuga ebidduka biyambye South Korea okukola ebigezo ebimu ebyangu era ebingi mu ggwanga.Mu Bugirimaani, ekibiina kya National Association of Health Insurance Statutory Physicians kyagamba nga March 2 nti kyali kisobola okukola ebigezo nga 12,000 buli lunaku mu ddwaaliro, nga 10,700 ze zaakolebwa wiiki ewedde.
Ssente zibalirirwa ku by'obulamu bw'oba oyagala okukeberebwa omusawo.
Okusinziira ku ssentebe wa Robert Koch Institute, Bugirimaani erina obusobozi bw'okunoonyereza 160,000 buli wiiki.
Okuva nga March 19, okugezesebwa mu ddereeva kwaweebwa mu bibuga ebinene.
Okuva nga 26 Maaki 2020, omuwendo gw'okugezesebwa okwakolebwa mu Bugirimaani gukyali mu butamanya, kubanga ebigezo ebirungi byokka bye biwandiisibwa.
Ekikeberebwa ekisooka kyalaga nti okuva wiiki 12 ey'omwaka 2020 ebitundu 483,295 byateekebwako ebipimo okutuusa wiiki 12 ey'omwaka 2020 era ebitundu 33,491 (6.9%) byazuulibwa nga birimu akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2. Mu Isiraeri, abanoonyereza okuva mu malwaliro ga Technion ne Rambam baakola era ne bagezaako enkola ey'okugezesa ebipimo by'abalwadde 64 mu kiseera kye kimu, nga bakuŋŋaanya ebipimo era ne bakola ebigezo ebirala singa ebipimo ebiyungiddwa byokka bye bibeera nga birimu akawuka. Mu Wuhan, ekikeberebwa eky'obudde eky'obubudamu ekya 2,000m2 ekiyitibwa "Huo-Yan" (Chinese: 火眼, oba "Fire Eye" mu Lungereza) kyasumululwa nga Febwali 5, 2020 ne BGI, ekisobola okukola ebipimo ebisukka mu 10,000 buli lunaku.
Nga bikola ku bulagirizi bw'oyo eyatandikawo BGI, Wang Jian, era nga kitwala ennaku 5, okukoppa kwalaga nti abalwadde mu Hubei bandibadde bangi 47% era nti ssente ez'okuddukanya ekikangabwa zandibadde zikubisaamu emirundi ebiri singa obuyinza obwo obw'okugezesa tebwali ku mutimbagano.
Ekimera kya Wuhan kyaddako ne kijjira mu kizimbe kya Huo-Yan mu Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, ne Shanghai, mu bibuga 12 mu China yonna.
Nga 4 March 2020, obuwumbi 50 obw'okugezesebwa buli lunaku bwabaddewo. Amamodeli ag'oku mutimbagano agaggulawo ensibuko agafulumiziddwa Origami Assays gafulumiziddwa nga gasobola okugezesa abalwadde 1,122 ku COVID-19 nga bakozesa ebigezo 93 byokka. Amamodeli gano agagudde olubege gasobola okukolebwa mu laboratories entono nga tewabaawo kyetaagisa bakugu ba robotic ku mazzi.
Mu March, ebbula oba ebbula ly'ekirungo lyafuuka ekiremesa okugezesa mu bungi mu European Union, UK ne US.
Kino kyaviirako abawandiisi abamu okunoonyereza ku nkola z'okwetegekera ebibala ezirimu okufumita ebibala ku 98 °C (208 °F) okumala eddakiika 5 okuggya genomes za RNA okusobola okugezesebwa. Ku 31 March, kyalagulwa nti UAE kati ekola ebigezo bingi ku buli muntu ku bantu baayo ku Corona Virus okusinga ensi endala, era nti eri mu kkubo ly'okwongera ku mutindo gw'okugezesa n'okuzuula abantu abasinga obungi.
Kino kyava ku kugatta wamu obusobozi bw'okuvuga, n'okufuna laboratory y'okukozesa abantu bangi okuva mu kibinja kya 42 ne BGI (ekyakubirizibwa laboratories zaayo ez'okunoonyereza ku bukyayi "Huo-Yan" mu China).
Eyategekebwa mu nnaku 14, laboratory esobola okukola enkumi n'enkumi z'ebigezo bya RT-PCR buli lunaku era y'ensi esooka mu bunene buno okukola ebweru wa China.
Enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okugezesa ezirimu ebitundu eby'enjawulo eby'obutonde bwa coronavirus zaakolebwa mu China, Bufalansa, Bugirimaani, Hong Kong, Japan ne Amerika.
Ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu ekya World Health Organization kyakozesa enkola ya Bugirimaani okukola ebizigo ebitwalibwa mu nsi eziri mu mbeera embi nga tezisobola kukola byazo.
Enkola y'omu Bugirimaani yatongozebwa nga January 17, 2020; enkola eyafulumizibwa ekitongole kya Amerika eky'okufuga endwadde teyaliwo okutuusa nga January 28, waaliwo okuteebereza ku bikeberebwa ebyaweebwa Amerika ne China era Amerika yafuna ebizibu ku kwesigika kw'ebikozesebwa mu kukebera abantu ku ntandikwa y'obulwadde, era ensi zino awamu ne Australia zaali tezisobola kuwa bantu bingi okusobola okutuukiriza obwetaavu n'ebiragiro by'abasawo.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, abakugu bagamba nti obwetaavu bwa South Korea obw'okugezesa buyambye okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa coronavirus empya.
Obusobozi bw'okugezesa, okusingira ddala mu laboratories ez'ebitongole eby'obwannannyini, bwateekebwawo okumala emyaka mingi gavumenti ya South Korea.
Nga Maaki 16, Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'Ensi Yonna kyagamba nti okwongera ku nteekateeka z'okugezesa y'engeri esingayo obulungi ey'okukendeeza ku kwongera kw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19. Okwetaaga okw'amaanyi okw'okugezesa olw'obulwadde obusaasaanye kuleetedde enkumi n'enkumi z'okugezesa mu laboratories ez'obwannannyini mu Amerika okusubwa, era n'okufuna ebikozesebwa mu kugaba n'ebikozesebwa mu by'obupangisa ne bikoseddwa.
