Kyokka, sabbuuni ezirwanyisa obuwuka zirimu eddagala erirwanyisa obuwuka, gamba nga triclosan, eririmu ebika by'ebiramu ebirwanyisa obuwuka.
N'olwekyo, wadde ng'ebirungo ebirwanyisa obuwuka tebisobola kukozesebwa mu sabbuuni ezirwanyisa obuwuka, biyinza obutaba bya maanyi nga bwe kigambibwa.
Ng'oggyeko ebikozesebwa mu kukyusa omubiri n'okukuuma olususu, enkola ez'enjawulo ziyinza okubaamu asidi (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid) ng'omutonzi wa pH, benzoic acid ey'obulabe, n'ebirala ebikuuma olususu (aloe vera, vitamin, menthol, ebirime). Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu yunivasite ya Oregon School of Public Health kwalaga nti sabbuuni eza bulijjo ziringa eza bakasitoma mu kuziyiza endwadde n'okuggyawo obuwuka ku mikono.
Amazzi agookya agabeera amalungi okunaaba mu ngalo tegaba gabugumu kimala okutta obuwuka.
Obuwuka bukula amangu ku bbugumu ly'omubiri (37 oC).
Kyokka, amazzi agookya n'omusaayi gaganyula nnyo mu kuggya amafuta agabeera mu mazzi ago ne gaviirako obuwuka obuli mu mubiri okubula.
Okwawukana ku ndowooza abantu bangi gye balina, naye, okunoonyereza kulaga nti okukozesa amazzi agookya tekivaamu kalungi konna ku bulwadde obuli ku mikono.
Ekimera ekikola ku ngalo oba ekirwanyisa obuwuka obufa ku ngalo kye kintu ekikola ku ngalo ekitalina mazzi.
Mu myaka gya 1990 n'omwaka gwa 2000 ogusooka, enkola y'okukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa non-water based alcohol hand hygiene agents (era emanyiddwa nga alcohol based hand hygiene product, antiseptic hand hygiene product, oba hand sanitizer) yatandika okugaziwa.
Ebisinga bikolebwa ku mwenge gwa isopropyl oba ethanol ogukoleddwa n'ekikonge, gamba nga carbomer (polymer oba acrylic acid), mu ggeeti, oba ekikonge, gamba nga glycerin, mu mazzi, oba mu busawo okusobola okuguyamba era n'okukendeeza ku bukoowu bwa mwenge.
Okugatta ku ekyo, omukka gwa hydrogen peroxide guyamba okulwanyisa obuwuka.
Abakozesa omwenge okusazaamu bafiirawo obuwuka, obuwuka obuziyiza omukka (MRSA ne REV), akafuba, n'akawuka akamu (nga mw'otwalidde HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinoviruses, vaccina, influenza ne hepatitis) ne fungi.
Abakozesa omwenge omungi okuli omwenge 70%, batta 99,97% (okukendeeza logarithm 3.5, okufaananako okukendeeza decibel 35) ku bulwadde ku mikono, mu ddakiika 30 oluvannyuma lw'okubakozesa, era 99.99% okutuuka ku 99,999% (okukendeeza logarithm 4-5) ku bulwadde ku mikono mu ddakiika emu oluvannyuma lw'okubakozesa.
Abakozesa omwenge mu kuyonja engalo tebalina mugaso gwonna ku kirwadde kya Norovirus (oba Norwalk), ekisinga okuleeta endwadde y'olukonvuba.
Emikono n'amabega, wakati w'engalo n'ebikondo by'engalo, bisasulwa okumala eddakiika nga 30 okutuusa ng'amazzi, enfuufu oba jjiimu bigudde.
Ensonga z'engalo nazo zirina okunaazibwa obulungi nga zikulukusibwa n'emikono gyombi. Ekitongole kya CDC kibuulirira okunaazibwa engalo n'amazzi ag'okukuuma engalo naddala ng'engalo zikooye.
Okukozesa okw'amaanyi kw'ebikozesebwa bino kwesigamye ku kuba nti byangu okukozesa era nti biyamba nnyo mu kuzikiriza obuwuka; kyokka, tebisaanidde kudda mu kifo ky'okunaaba engalo obulungi okuggyako ng'amasavu n'amazzi tebiriiwo.
Okukozesa ennyo enjaga ey'oku mikono kiyinza okuviirako olususu okuzimbulukuka okuggyako nga emollients ne/oba enfuufu ez'olususu ziyongereddwa mu pulaani.
Okuba nti omwenge guba gwaka nnyo kiyinza okukendeezebwako oba okuggibwawo ng'ogatta ku glycerin ne/oba ebintu ebirala ebiwunyiriza ku pulaani.
Mu kugezesebwa kwa ddwaliro, enjaga ey'okuyonja engalo erimu ebirungo yabaleetera okukaaba n'okukaaba ennyo okusinga sabbuuni oba eddagala erigema obuwuka.
Obulwadde bw'ensusu obuyitibwa allergic contact dermatitis, contact urticaria syndrome, oba obuwuka obuyitibwa hypersensitivity eri omwenge oba ebikozesebwa mu by'okukozesa mu kuyonja engalo.
Okutwalirizibwa okutereera okw'okukubiriza dermatitis ey'okukwata n'okulumya abantu kwe kwafuuka okw'omugaso okusinga okunaaba engalo n'amazzi n'amasavu.
Wadde nga bikola bulungi, eddagala eritali lya mazzi terisaanuusa ngalo z'ebiramu, wabula liziwonya.
Eno y'ensonga lwaki eddagala erigonjoola ebiwuka terikola bulungi ng'amazzi n'ensabbu mu kuziyiza endwadde nnyingi okusaasaana kubanga endwadde zikyali ku mikono.
Obuwanguzi bw'eby'okukozesa mu kuyonja engalo ebitalina mwenge bwesigamye nnyo ku bintu n'enkola, era mu byafaayo buva ku mwenge n'eby'okukozesa mu kuyonja engalo ebirimu mwenge.
Gye buvuddeko awo, enkola ezikozesa benzalkonium chloride zaalabiddwa ng'ezina ekikolwa eky'okulwanyisa obuwuka obufa ku bantu nga zikyaliwo oluvannyuma lw'okuzikozesa, okwawukana ku mwenge, ogulabiddwa ng'ogutabaako mugaso oluvannyuma lw'okukozesebwa enfunda n'enfunda, oboolyawo olw'obulwadde obw'olusu.
Abantu bangi mu bitundu omuli abantu abatalina ssente nnyingi tebasobola kusasula sabbuuni, era mu kifo kyayo bakozesa evvu oba ettaka.
Ensimbi oba ettaka biyinza okuba nga bikola bulungi okusinga amazzi amayonjo, naye biyinza okuba nga tebikola bulungi okusinga sabbuuni.
Ekimu ku biyinza okweraliikiriza kiri nti singa ettaka oba evvu likyonoonese, obulwadde busobola okweyongera mu kifo ky'okudda wansi.
Okufaananako sabbuuni, envunyu nayo ekola ng'ekyuma ekirwanyisa obutwa kubanga bw'ekwata ku mazzi eba ng'envunyu.
Ekitongole kya WHO kiwa amagezi nti enfuufu n'omusenyu biyinza okudda mu kifo ky'ensawo singa tewali nsawo.
Enkola entuufu ey'okunaaba engalo ng'ekitebe kya Amerika ekirwanyisa endwadde bwe kigaana abantu obutafuna ndwadde, erimu ebintu bino wammanga:
Koola engalo zo n'amazzi agannyogoga oba agannyogoga.
