Bw'oba olina ensonga ey'ekyama oba ey'obutebenkevu, tuma obubaka ku Bryan Judan, akulira emirimu gya HR mu nsi yonna.
Tewali n'emu ku nkyukakyuka zino eyanditutte ng'okuleka emirimu gyaffe n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe.
Kyokka, kino kiraga nti mu kiseera kino emirimu gyaffe n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe bijja kwetaaga okukyusibwa mu ngeri gye tutakikolamu mu biseera ebyayita.
Bino bye bintu bye tulowooza nti byetaagisa okusobola okubayamba mu kiseera kino, tusobole okweyongera okukola, okuwa ekibiina kyaffe obuyambi bwe kyetaaga, n'okuwa ensi obuweereza bw'esobola okufuna.
Omulimu gwaffe ogutegekeddwa gujja kuba gutuliriridde ng'ekiseera kituuse.
Mu kiseera kino, kye kiseera okuwagana n'okuteekawo ekifo eky'okukola omulimu omukulu ogujja okukolebwa mu wiiki eziddako, era oboolyawo n'emyezi egijja.
Twetaaga mwenna okubayamba okukola kino, era twetaaga buli omu okulabirira amaka gammwe n'okukuuma obulamu bwammwe nga bwe busobola.
Munaabe engalo zammwe era temukwata ku maaso gammwe!
Katherine, ekibinja ky'eby'empuliziganya (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, ne Tony S), n'abalala bonna mu kibinja ky'obukulembeze (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, ne Toby N).
Enzimu eyitibwa angiotensin-converting enzyme type 2 (ECA2) y'enziramu ekwatagana n'ebitundu eby'ennyindo (ebisenge by'amasero) mu bitundu by'omutima, emitwe, empiso, ne mu lubuto.
ECA2 ekendeeza ku bikolwa bya angiotensin-related enzyme (ACE) ng'ekendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin II n'okuyimusa Ang (1-7), n'ekifuula eddagala eryasuubizibwa erijjanjaba endwadde z'omutima. ECA2 era ekola ng'ekifo ekirimu obuterekebwa mu butoffaali bwa koronavairusi ezimu.
Enzimu eyo ey'omu bantu etera okuyitibwa hECA2.
Enzimu ey'engeri ey'okubiri ey'okufuula angiotensin, y'enziramu erimu zinc eri ku ntobo y'omubiri n'ensulo endala.
ECA2 erimu ekitundu kya peptidase M2 eky'oku N-terminal n'ekitundu kya C-terminal ekisangibwa mu nsigo.
ECA2 ye proteini eya membrane type 1 ey'olugendo lumu, nga ekitundu kyayo ekikolera ku by'ensulo kibeera ku bitundu by'omubiri mu biwundu ne mu bitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ECA2 ekisangibwa wabweru w'enseke kiwandikawo okuva ku kitundu kya transmembrane ne enzyme endala eyitibwa sheddase, era enfuna ya protein esobola okuvunda n'efulumizibwa mu musaayi era n'evunda.
ECA2 eri mu bitundu bingi: ECA2 ekwatagana ne ssimu y'ensulo z'ensulo ez'amaanyi ez'omu lubuto ez'ekika II, enterocytes ez'omubiri omutono, endothelial cells ez'omu musaayi n'ez'omu musaayi mu bitundu ebisinga obungi.
ECA2 mRNA eyogerwa era esangibwa mu bwongo, mu mubiri oguli mu ngeri ey'ekikaba, mu hypothalamus, ne mu bwongo.
Ekimu ku bintu ECA2 by'esinga okukola kwe kufuba okuziyiza ECA.
EKT ekwata ku angiotensin I n'ekifuula angiotensin II ne kiviirako okutabula kw'omusaayi.
ECA2 nayo esobola okusala ensimbi okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) n'eyingiza ensimbi mu angiotensin ey'omusaayi (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 era esobola okusalako peptide endala ezitali zimu, omuli [des-Arg9]- bradicinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, ne ghrelin.
ECA2 era ekubiriza okutambuza amayinja mu lususu lwa SLC6A19 era erina akakwate n'obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'ekimera ekirimu ekirungo ekikuuma omubiri, ECA2 ekola ng'ekifo ekikulu eky'okuyingira mu butoffaali bwa koronavairusi ezimu, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akooleka SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akooleka COVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, okukwata protein ya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 S1 ku ECA2 enzyme domain ku ttaka ly'ensulo kivaamu endocytosis n'okukyusa akawuka n'enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu masero.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa enkola ya protein S okuteekebwawo omulabirizi wa TMPRSS2 serine protease, ekirwadde kino kye kyetaaga okutangirirwa era kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ECA2 mu mubiri kiyinza okuyamba okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'obuweereza n'ebitongole ebifuga eby'obujjanjabi bikubirizza okweyongera n'enkola y'okuziyiza obulwadde bwa AED n'eddagala lya BRA.
Okunoonyereza n'okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku Lwakubiri nga July 11, 2012 kwalaga nti "okukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa ACE inhibitors kyaleetera omuntu okufuna obulwadde bwa kkansa nga 34% okusinga ab'ekika ekirala".
Ate era, "obutebenkevu bw'omusujja gw'amawuggwe nabwo bwawongezebwa mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa eddagala eriyitibwa ACE inhibitors abaalina obwetaavu bw'omusujja gw'amawuggwe, naddala abo abalina sitayiro n'omutima ogutazimba.
Okukozesa ACE inhibitors nakwo kwagattibwa ku kukendeeza okufa okw'obulwadde bwa pneumonia, wadde nga ebyavuddeyo byali tebikyali bya maanyi nnyo ng'ebyo eby'obulabe bwa pneumonia bwonna.'
ECA2 ey'omubiri (rhACE2) ekkirizibwa okuba obujjanjabi obuggya obw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, era kirabika y'eyongedde okulongoosa obusimu bw'amawuggwe n'okusaasaanya omukka mu mbizzi ezirina obulwadde bw'obutafuna mutawaana mu bulamu.
RhACE2 erina ekitundu ky'ekiseera ky'obulamu mu bantu eky'essaawa nga 10 era okutandika kw'ekikolwa kwa ddakiika 30 oluvannyuma lw'ebiseera by'ebiseera 24 (ebiseera by'obulamu).
Ebintu bingi ebisangibwa biraga nti rhACE2 esobola okuba eddagala eririmu essuubi eri abo abatalina buvunanyizibwa ku ddagala eriyitibwa classical renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) oba endwadde ezirimu endwadde eziyitiridde.
Enkola za COVID-19 ze programu za ssimu ez'okuyambako mu kulondoola olw'ekirwadde kya coronavirus 2019-2020, kwe kugamba, enkola y'okumanya abantu ("abafaanana") abaasobola okuba nga baakwatagana n'abantu abalina obulwadde.
Enkola nnyingi zaakolebwa oba zaaweebwa obuyambi okuva mu gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu.
Ebibiina bingi eby'okuzimba enkola z'okukebera abakwatagana byafulumizibwa.
Ebibuuzo by'obwannannyini byaleetebwawo, naddala ku nkola ezisinziira ku kunoonyereza ku kifo abakozesa programu gye bali.
Enkyusa ezitali za buzibu zizingiramu okukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ku ssimu endala.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple baategeezezza nti bajja kussaawo obusobozi okuwagira programu ng'ezo ez'oku mutimbagano ogwa Bluetooth ku nkola zaabwe ez'okuweereza Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti ya China awamu ne Alipay batandisewo programu esobozesa abantu okukebera oba nga baatuukiddwako omuntu alina COVID-19.
Kati ekozesebwa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 mu China, ate mu Singapore, enkola eyitibwa TraceTogether ekozesebwa.
Enkola eno yateekebwawo ekibiina kya IT ekya local, yafulumizibwa nga open source era ejja kuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yatandikawo "StopKorona!", enkola ekozesa Bluetooth okukebera abantu abalina obulwadde n'okuyamba ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu.
App eno yateekebwawo minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'entekinologiya ne minisitule y'ebyobulamu.
Okuva nga 14 April 2020, app yali esembedde okukkirizibwa okuva ku Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 omwezi gwa April, gavumenti yagamba nti app y'okunoonyereza ku bantu yali mu mitendera egy'amaanyi mu kukulaakulana, era nti yandibadde efuna okugabibwa mu wiiki. App efaananako bw'etyo eteekeddwa okubeera mu Ireland, ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand biteekateeka enkola ezesigamiziddwa ku Singapore's TraceTogether app ne BlueTrace protocol. Russia eteekateeka okutandikawo enkola ey'okusiba enkola y'okulonda abalwadde abalina COVID-19 ababeera mu Moscow, ekitegekeddwa okukakasa nti tebasula waka.
Ross Anderson, profesa wa by'obunjiniya mu byokwerinda mu yunivasite ya Cambridge, yabala ebizibu bingi eby'omugaso mu nkola eziriko enkola ez'okuteeka mu nkola, omuli obulimba n'obutabaako mugaso singa enkola ekkirizibwa abantu batono.
Mu kugonjoola okweraliikirira ku kubuna kwa 'coronavirus' ez'obulimba oba ez'akabi, Apple eteeka ekkomo ku bika by'ebitongole ebiyinza okwongera ku 'coronavirus' ezikwata ku App Store, nga zibikugira ku bitongole 'eby'obuyinza' oba ebisaanira.
Google ne Amazon nabyo byateekawo obukwakkulizo obufaanana.
Abakuuma ddembe ly'obuntu boogedde ku ngeri abantu gye bayinza okulabirirwamu nga bakozesa programu za coronavirus, naddala obanga ebyuma ebikuuma ddembe ebyakolebwa okuziyiza ekirwadde kya coronavirus bijja kuggibwawo ng'obutiini buweddewo.
Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisukka mu 100 baafulumizza ekiteeso nga basaba okukomya okulondoola kuno.
Ebibiina byategeezezza embeera munaana ez'okuyingira mu mirimu gya gavumenti:
Okulabirira kwandibadde 'kwa mateeka, okwetaagisa era nga kwa bwenkanya';
okuwanjulibwa kw'okulondoola n'okwetegereza kwandibadde n'ebiragiro eby'okuyimiriza;
okukozesa obubaka kulina kukomekkerezebwa ku bigendererwa bya COVID-19;
Obukuumi n'obuteyogerako kw'ebikwata ku bantu byandibadde bikuumibwa era ne bibeera nga bikuumibwa ku bukakafu.
Okulabirira kwa digito kulina okwewala okusosola n'okusosolwa.
Okugabana kwonna kw'eby'obuntu n'abantu abalala kwandibadde kuteekeddwa mu mateeka;
Basaanidde okuba n'obukuumi ku bikolwa eby'obukambwe n'eddembe ly'abantu okuddamu nga bayisiddwa obubi;
Okuyingiza obuyambi obutaliimu okuva mu 'bakwate bonna abakulu' kyetaagisa, omuli abakugu mu by'obulamu n'ebibinja ebirese abantu ku bunkenke.
Enteekateeka eyalagiddwa Google/Apple etegeeza okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okwetegereza okw'enkalakkalira nga baggyako enkola y'okutambuza ebintu okuva ku nkola zaabwe ezikozesa ebyuma nga tekikyali kyetaagisa.
Amawanga agamu gaakozesa enkola ey'okuzuula ebifo ng'eyita mu mukutu mu kifo ky'okuzuula programu, ne kiba nti tewaaliwo kyetaagisa kugiggyamu era ne kiba nti tewaaliwo busobozi bwa kugiggyamu.
Mu Isiraeri, okulondoola okusinziira ku mikutu gya Internet kukkiriziddwa.
Enkola ez'oku mutimbagano ezirina enkola y'okuzuula ebifo ebikalu zirina obuzibu bwa maanyi obw'obuntu.
Kyokka, si buli nkola erina omuserikale omukulu eyetaaga okufuna obubaka ku kifo ky'omuntu; enkola ezimu ezikuuma obukuumi zaakolebwa okukozesa omuserikale omukulu okuwuliziganya kyokka (laba akatundu ak'omunsi).
Mu South Korea, enkola etaali ya mu nkola yakozesebwa okukola okunoonyereza ku muntu.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa programu emu yokka, enkola eno yategeka obubaka obw'okunoonya okuva mu nsi nnyingi, omuli obubaka bw'okuzuula ebyuma ebikozesebwa ku ssimu n'obw'okukozesa kaadi, n'ebikwataganya okuleeta okulabula okuyitira mu bubaka obw'obubaka eri abantu abayinza okuba n'obulwadde.
Ng'oggyeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abantu, gavumenti era ekoze obubaka bw'ekifo okuweebwa abantu bonna, ekikkirizibwa olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu mateeka ag'obukuumi bw'obubaka oluvannyuma lw'ekirwadde kya MERS mu ggwanga.
Amagezi gano gali mu bantu bonna okuyita mu programu n'emikutu gya Internet. Amawanga, omuli ne Bugirimaani, gatunuulira okukozesa enkola y'okukuuma obukuumi n'ey'okukuuma obukuumi.
Nga 6 April 2020 ebintu tebinnategerekeka.
Okukebera omuntu nga tukuuma obukuumi kye kigambo ekimanyiddwa obulungi, nga waliwo ebitabo bingi eby'obumanyirivu okuva mu 2013. Okuva nga April 7, 2020, ebibinja by'abakugu ebisukka mu kkumi na bibiri bibadde bikolera ku ngeri y'okukuuma obukuumi, nga bikozesa Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ku masimu amalala.
Kyokka, PEPP-PT y'omulimu gw'okukulembera oguzingiramu enkola ez'obukiiko n'ez'obukiiko, so si nkola emu. Enkola ez'obukiiko zirimu Decentralized privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN) Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'endala.
Mu nkola zino, obubaka obumanyiddwa ku muntu tebuva ku kyuma, era buli kikwatagana kikolebwa ku kyuma.
Ekibinja kya Privacy Group mu MIT Media Lab kibadde kikola ku Safe Paths, ekitebe eky'okukozesa enkola ez'okukuuma obuntu nga bakuŋŋaanya era nga bakozesa obubaka bw'ekifo oba obw'okuyita mu kkubo okunoonyereza ku kusaasaana kwa COVID-19.
Kisinziira ku kunoonyereza okuva mu kiwandiiko ekikwata ku nkola ya tekinologiya ekirina omutwe "Apps Play Dirty: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" ekyafulumizibwa mu March 2020.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya wa hardware omunywevu okusobozesa abakozesa okugabana obubaka obw'obuzibu obw'ekifo n'obulamu n'abakozesa abalala n'abakulembeze nga tebukosa bwekubiira.
Nga 5 Apuli 2020, Global TCN Coalition yatandikibwawo ebibinja ebigatta ku ngeri y'emu era nga bingi ku byo birimu enkola ez'enjawulo, nga kigendererwa kya kugabanyaamu obutakkaanya, n'okusobozesa okukolera awamu kw'obulabirizi n'okukebera, ekintu ekikulu mu kutuuka ku kukkiriza abantu bangi.
Nga 9 April 2020, gavumenti ya Singapore yalangirira nti enkola ya BlueTrace, ekozesebwa mu nkola ya gavumenti, kati ya ddungu liggule.
Nga 10 omwezi gwa April, 2020, Google ne Apple, amakampuni agafuga emikutu gya Android ne iOS, gaalangirira enteekateeka y'okunoonyereza ku mikwano gyabwe, mwe baagambye nti bajja kukuuma obukuumi, nga basinziira ku kukozesa tekinologiya wa Bluetooth Low Energy n'okuwandiisa okusobola okukuuma obukuumi.
Era baafulumya n'obutegeeza ku tekinologiya omukulu ogukozesebwa mu nkola eno.
Okusinziira ku Apple ne Google, enkola eteekateeka okutandikibwawo mu mitendera esatu:
Okukulaakulanya ebyuma okuleka gavumenti okutandikawo enkola ez'obuyinza ez'okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe nga bakuuma obukuumi
okugatta obusobozi buno butereevu mu iOS ne Android; Google ne Apple bateekateeka okulwanyisa ebizibu by'okwetegereza ebyeyongedde n'ebitwala nga basooka kugabira enteekateeka nga bongera ku nkola ezikola, era oluvannyuma ne bagiggyawo mu ngeri y'emu ng'akabi kaguddewo.
Okuddaabiriza eddagala (era okumanyibwa nga okuddaabiriza eddagala, okuddaabiriza, okuddaabiriza, oba okuddaabiriza eddagala) kwe kuddamu okuddaabiriza eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba embeera y'ekisawo oba obulwadde obw'enjawulo ku eyo gye lyakolebwa.
Guno gwe gumu ku misingi gy'okunoonyereza mu bya sayansi ogukyaliwo mu kiseera kino okutandikawo obujjanjabi obumatiza era obw'omuganyulo ku COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza okulala kuzingiramu okwekulaakulanya omusaayi ogusobola okuwona n'ekirwadde kya COVID-19. SARS-CoV-2 erina obutoffaali nga 66 obuyinza okukozesebwa, nga buli bumu buliko ebifo bingi eby'okusiba.
Okwekenneenya ebifo bino eby'okusiba kiwa ekiruubirirwa ekituufu eky'okuzimba eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka akawuka ka mukenenya erirwanyisa obutoffaali bwa COVID-19.
Mu bupolyeteni obusinga obukulu obugenderwa SARS-CoV-2 mwe muli papain-like protease, RNA polymerase, helicase, protein S, ne ADP ribophosphatease.
Hussein A. A., et al., beekenneenya eddagala erimu eryali lisobola okuteekebwa mu nkola era ne likola ku ngeri gye lifaananamu n'eddagala eryali lifaanana eryo okusobola okwanguya okukulaakulanya eddagala ery'amaanyi erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 mu kunoonyereza kwabwe okwali kuwedde.
Chloroquine ddagala erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri era lirina ebikozesebwa okulwanyisa endwadde ezimu ez'obutafa.
Nga 18 March, WHO yalangirira nti chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine ez'enjawulo zandibadde mu ddagala ennya ezinoonyerezebwa ng'ekitundu ky'okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa Solidarity.
Gavana wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okunoonyereza ku chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine mu New York State kujja kutandika nga March 24. Nga March 28, FDA yalagira okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne chloroquine phosphate nga bayita mu Emergency Use Authorization (AUE).
Endowooza eno teyasiimibwa FDA mu nkola y'okunoonyereza era ekkirizibwa okuyita mu AUE ng'eddagala ery'okunoonyereza lyokka ery'okukozesa mu bwangu mu balwadde abali mu ddwaliro abatayinza kufuna ddagala mu kugezesebwa.
CDC yagamba nti "okukozesa, eddagala, oba ebbanga ly'omwenge gwa hydroxychloroquine olw'okutangira oba okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2" tekinnategeerekeka.
Abasawo bagamba nti bakozesa eddagala lino nga "tebalina kya kwekolera".
Mu Istanbul, ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza eky'omu Turkey kikoze okunoonyereza okutono ku kukozesa chloroquine awamu ne zinc, vitamin A, vitamin C, ne vitamin D.
Okunoonyereza okunene kugenda mu maaso ku yunivasite ya Duke ne Oxford.
Langone School of Medicine ey'omu NYU ekola okunoonyereza ku bukuumi n'obwanguzi bw'okukozesa hydroxychloroquine mu ngeri ey'okutangira obulwadde.
Okugezesebwa kw'ekinnansi mu China mu Wuhan ne Shenzhen kwagamba nti okulaga nti favipiravir yali "n'omugaso".
Mu Shenzhen, abalwadde 35 baalabika nga tebalina bulwadde mu nnaku 4 nga bwe kiba kya bulijjo, ate abalwadde 45 abataalina bulwadde baamala ennaku 11.
Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu Wuhan ku balwadde 240 abalina omusujja gw'amawuggwe, kimu kya kubiri kyaweebwa favipiravir, ate ekirala kimu kyaweebwa umifenovir.
Ekitongole kya Italy ekivunaanyizibwa ku by'eddagala kijjukizza abantu nti obujulizi obuliwo okuwagira eddagala lino butono era bwa kusooka.
Nga Apuli 2, Bugirimaani yalangirira nti yali agenda kugula eddagala okuva mu Japan okulikozesa era akozese amagye okuliyisa mu malwaliro ga yunivasite, mwe lyandibadde likozesebwa okujjanjaba abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Okusinziira ku South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe abadde awa gavumenti ya Trump obukakafu ku kugula eddagala lino. Eddagala lino liyinza obutakola bulungi mu balwadde ab'amaanyi, nga akawuka kaakula.
Okukozesa eddagala lino kiyinza obutaba kya bukuumi eri abakazi ab'embuto oba abagezaako okufuna olubuto.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku lupinavir/ ritonavir (Kaletra), eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka ka lupinavir ne ritonavir, kwalaga nti "tewali mugaso gwonna ogulabikira".
Eddagala lino lyakolebwa okuziyiza okukulaakulana kwa siriimu nga ligatta ku protease.
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza ku Yunivasite ya Colorado bagezaako okukyusa eddagala okufuna ekika ekinyweza protease ya SARS-CoV-2. Waliwo okwemulugunya mu bannasayansi ku kuggya eby'obugagga ku ddagala eryazuulibwa ku HIV/AIDS.
WHO yatwala lopinavir/ritonavir mu kigezo kya Solidarity ekya nsi yonna.
Remdesivir yatondebwa era n'okufuulibwa Gilead Sciences ng'eddagala erijjanjaba ekirwadde kya Ebola ne Marburg virus. Gilead Sciences yakizuula oluvannyuma nti remdesivir erina ebikolwa eby'okulwanyisa akawuka ka mukenenya mu vitro eri phylum, pneumonia, paramyxoma ne coronaviruses.
Ekimu ku bizibu ebiva mu bujjanjabi bwa HIV kwe kukyusa mu ngeri gye bukolamu ne kiviirako abantu okufuna endwadde ez'amaanyi.
Okunoonyereza okusooka kulaga nti remdesivir esobola okuba n'omuggalo omunene ogw'obusobozi bw'okuziyiza. Waliwo okugezesebwa kwa mirundi ebiri mu maaso, omuli okugezesebwa kwa mirundi ebiri okukolebwa Cleveland University Hospitals, omu ku bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi ate omulala ku abo abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Waliwo okugezesebwa kwa ddagala kwa vitamini C okusatu okukolebwa ku bantu abali mu ddwaliro era abalwadde ennyo COVID-19: bibiri ku byo bya placebo (mu China ne Canada), ate ekirala tekirina kibiina kya bufuzi (Italy).
