Mu Gangelt, obulwadde bwabuna ku mbaga za Carnival era ne busaasaana mu bantu abato, ne kiviirako okufa okutono, era si buli muntu eyafa COVID-19 nti yawandiikibwa mu butongole.
Ate era, embeera y'obulamu mu Bugirimaani teyali nzibu nnyo.
Mu Netherlands, abantu nga 3% bayinza okuba n'omubiri ogumeggana, nga bwe kiragibwa mu bantu abawadde omusaayi.
69 (0,004% ku bantu) bakakasibwa okufa COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino n'omuwendo gw'abafa byawukana ku basajja n'abakazi.
Okufa kwabwe kusingawo mu basajja mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu China ne Italy.
Obuzibu obusinga eri abasajja bubeera mu myaka gya 50, ng'enjawulo wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi esembera emyaka 90 gyokka.
Mu China, omuwendo gw'abafa gwali wa bitundu 2.8 ku buli kikumi ku basajja n'ebitundu 1.7 ku buli kikumi ku bakazi.
Ensonga ez'enkukunala ezireetera enjawulo wakati w'ekikula n'ekya mukazi tezimanyiddwa, naye obuzaale n'enneeyisa biyinza okuba nga bye bireetera.
Enjawulo mu by'omubiri olw'ekikula, abakyala okunywa ssigala n'abasajja okufuna endwadde nga puleesa y'omusaayi nga bakyali bato okusinga abakazi, biyinza okuba nga byaviirako abasajja okufa.
Mu Bulaaya, 57% ku bantu abafunye obulwadde baali basajja, ate 72% ku baafa COVID-19 baali basajja.
Okutuusa mu Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Amerika yali teyeetegereza bubaka ku bulwadde bwa COVID-19 obukwata ku kwegatta.
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti endwadde ez'obulabe gamba nga Ebola, HIV, ekikulukuto, ne SARS zikwata ku basajja n'abakazi mu ngeri za njawulo.
Abasuubuzi b'ebyobulamu abasinga obungi, naddala bannamukadde, bakazi, era be basinga okuteekebwawo akawuka.
Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'Ensi Yonna kyalangirira nga Febwali 11, 2020, nti erinnya ly'ekirwadde erya bulijjo lyali "COVID-19".
Akulira ekitongole kya WHO, Tedros Adhanon Ghebreyesus, yannyonnyodde nti "CO" kitegeeza "korona", "VI", kitegeeza "akawuka", "D" kitegeeza bulwadde ate "19" kitegeeza lwe kyazuulibwa: nga 31 December 2019.
Erinnya lyalondebwa okwewala okwogerako ku kifo ekimu (ng'ekyokulabirako, China), ekika ky'ensolo, oba abantu, okusinziira ku magezi g'ensi yonna ag'okuyita abantu okwewala okuvumirira. Akakoko akaviirako COVID-19 kayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO era ekozesa "akawuka ka COVID-19" ne "akawuka akaviirako COVID-19" mu kubuulira abantu.
Obulwadde n'akawuka byombi biyitibwa "coronavirus".
Mu kiseera eky'okusaasaana okwasooka mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byayitibwanga "coronavirus" ne "coronavirus ya Wuhan".
Mu January 2020, WHO yasalawo "2019-nCov" ne " 2019-nCoV acute respiratory disease" okuba amannya ag'ekiseera ag'akawuka n'obulwadde, nga bwe kyali mu bulagirizi bwa 2015 obukwata ku kukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'endwadde n'akawuka.
Amannya g'ekinnansi COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gaafulumizibwa nga Febwali 11, 2020.
Olw'obutaba na busobozi mu bifo ebikalu, abazannyi abamu mu bya digito baakuba ebiwandiiko eby'obujjanjabi, gamba ng'ebisenge by'omu nnyindo n'ebitundu by'ebyuma eby'okuwummulamu.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, eddwaliro ly'omu Italy bwe lyali lyetaaga nnyo vvulopu y'omukka oguwa omuntu amaanyi, era ng'oyo eyaguwa yali tasobola kugiwa mu kiseera ekituufu, ekitongole ekimu ekyaggulawo amaduuka mu kitundu ekyo kyabaako ne ky'ekikola ne kifulumya vvulopu 100 ezaali zeetaagisa mu lunaku lumu.
Oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kwa COVID-19, endowooza z'obukumpanya, obubaka obutali butuufu, n'obutamanya ku nsibuko, obunene, okutangira, okujjanjaba n'ebintu ebirala eby'obulwadde byabalukawo, era ne bisaasaana mangu ku Internet.
Kirabika abantu basobola okuleeta akawuka ku nsolo endala.
Okunoonyereza tekwasobola kusanga bujulizi bwa virus okuzaala mu mbizzi, enkaayi n'enkoko.
Tewali ddagala oba bulwadde obukkirizibwa okujjanjaba obulwadde buno.
Okunoonyereza okw'ensi yonna ku ddagala n'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kugenda mu maaso mu bitongole bya gavumenti, ebibiina by'abasomi n'abanoonyereza mu makolero.
Mu March, Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'Ensi Yonna kyatandikawo "Okutendekebwa kw'Obuyambi" okukebera ebikolwa by'obujjanjabi obw'ebintu bina ebirwanyisa akawuka ebiyinza okuba nga bikyasinga obulungi.
Tewali ddagala lirina kukozesebwa, naye ebitongole bingi bikola nnyo mu kutandika eddagala erigenda okuteekebwamu eddagala.
Ebyafaayo ku SARS-CoV bikozesebwa kubanga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 bikozesa ACE2 okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu.
Waliwo enkola ssatu ez'okulwanyisa endwadde ezinoonyerezebwako.
Okusooka, abanoonyereza baagala okuteekawo eddagala eririmu akawuka ako.
Okukozesa akawuka kano, ka kube nga tekakolebwako oba nga kafiiriddwa, kigendererwa kya kuleetawo okwanukula okw'omubiri okw'amangu ku bulwadde obuggya obw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19.
Enkola ey'okubiri, eddagala erikola ku butundutundu, erina ekigendererwa eky'okuteekawo eddagala erisobozesa obulwadde okukwata ku butundutundu bwa kawuka.
Ku nsonga ya SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza kuno kwesigamye ku proteini y'omu nsiri eyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Enkola eyokusatu y'ekikozesebwa mu bulwadde bwa nucleic acid (DNA oba RNA, enkola empya ey'okufuula obulwadde).
Okugezaako okulwanyisa obulwadde buno kwandibadde kukakasibwa nti bulwadde tebukosa era nti bulina obukakafu. Nga 16, Maaki 2020, okugezesebwa okwasooka okw'ekirwadde kya katemba kwatandika n'abantu bana mu Seattle.
Ekirwadde kino kiva ku bulwadde bwa SSARS-CoV-2 obuyitibwa SARS-CoV-2 ne SARS-CoV-2 obuyitibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Waliwo okugezesebwa kwa ddwaaliro okusukka mu 300 okwaliwo okuva mu Apuli 2020.
Ebigezo musanvu byekenneenya obujjanjabi obwakkirizibwa edda ku ndwadde ya malaria, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebirala bina eby'eddagala eriyitibwa hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Okuddaabiriza eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka kikola ekisinga ku kunoonyereza kwa China, nga remdesivir erina empaka mwenda ez'omugaso mu nsi ezitali zimu okusinziira ku alipoota eyafulumizibwa ku nkomerero ya Apuli.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi ku nkulaakulana y'eddagala n'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kwali kugenda mu maaso mu Apuli 2020.
Waliwo okugezaako okulaga nti remdesivir ekola okuva mu Maaki 2020.
Obulungi bw'ekika bwalabikira mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa remdesivir olw'okukozesa obulungi.
Okugezesebwa kw'ekibinja eky'okusatu mu Amerika, China ne Italy, Chloroquine, ekozesebwa eddagala lya malaria, yasomesebwa mu China mu Febwali 2020 n'ebivudde mu kusooka.
Kyokka waliwo okusaba okw'okukebera kuno.
Abakugu mu by'obulamu mu Korea ne China bakubiriza okukozesa chloroquine.
Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Virology Institute, wadde nga kyogera ku ddagala erimu erya gramu emu buli lunaku, kilabudde nti eddagala eryo erisingawo emirundi ebiri lya kabi nnyo era liyinza okutta.
Nga 28 Maaki 2020, FDA yafulumya olukusa olw'okukozesa hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine mu bwangu nga abasawo abajjanjaba abantu abalina COVID-19 bwe baagala. Ekitabo eky'omusanvu eky'obulagirizi bwa China era kizingiramu interferon, ribavirin oba umifenovir okukozesebwa ku COVID-19.
Ebyafaayo biraga nti eddagala eriyitibwa ribavirin eringi lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu malaalo.
Nitazoxanide yakubirizibwa okwongera okunoonyereza mu bulamu oluvannyuma lw'okulaga obuwuka bwa SARS-CoV-2 obutali bwa maanyi. Okunoonyereza kulaga nti protein y'ekika kya ssennyiga ey'olubereberye mu kuteekateeka kwa serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) nkulu nnyo mu kuyingira kwa SARS-CoV-2 ng'eyita mu ACE2.
Okunoonyereza ku chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine nga n'azithromycin oba nedda, birina obuzibu bungi obulemesa abasawo okutandika okuzikozesa nga tebannaba kunoonyereza. Oseltamivir teziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro era terina mulimu gwonna gw'ekola mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Kibuyaga wa cytokine ayinza okuba ekizibu mu mitendera egy'oluvannyuma egy'akabi ka COVID-19.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine esobola okuba n'ebika bya cytokine anti-storm. Tocilzumab yayingizibwa mu bulagirizi bw'obujjanjabi okuva mu National Health Commission of China oluvannyuma lw'okumaliriza okunoonyereza okutono.
Okugezesebwa okw'omuddiriŋŋanwa okw'omuddiriŋŋanwa okw'omugaso ogwa 2 mu ggwanga mu Italy kugenda mu maaso oluvannyuma lw'okulaga ebivudde mu bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Bwe kikwataganyizibwa n'okugezesebwa kw'omusaayi gwa serum ferritin okunoonyereza ku bubenje bwa cytokine, kisuubirwa okulemesa ebikolwa bino, ebisuubirwa okutta abantu abamu abakwatibwako.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yakkirizibwa FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde bwa steroid-refractory cytokine release syndrome obuleetebwa ekiruubirirwa ekirala, CAR T cell therapy mu 2017.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bukakafu bwonna bulaga nti tocilzumab ya mugaso mu kujjanjaba SRS.
Okuyingizaamu ebirwadde ebirwanyisa ekirwadde kino mu bantu ababyetaaga nga bakozesa eddagala eritali lya kkanso, okunoonyereza ku ngeri y'okuteekebwamu obulwadde buno.
Enkola eno yagezeseddwa ku SARS, naye n'ebyavaamu tebyali birungi.
Okuggyawo akawuka y'engeri y'okukikolamu ekisuubirwa nti eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka ka mukenenya liyinza okuteekawo obukuumi ku SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enkola endala, gamba ng'obutabaako nsawo za mubiri ezirwanyisa obulwadde bw'amasannyalaze n'obutonde, n'obutonde, zisobola okubaawo.
Engeri endala ez'okujjanjaba n'omubiri ogumu, gamba ng'okukozesa omubiri ogumu ogukozesebwa mu kukola eddagala, zeezze zitandika okukolebwa.
Okufulumya eddagala erigenda okuwona, eririmu omusaayi gw'abalwadde abawonye era eririmu ebirwanyisa ekirwadde kino, kiyinza okuzzibwamu amaanyi okusobola okukikola mu bwangu.
